%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20psyche%20and%20strategy%20of%20Modi%20if%20we%20are%20to%20contest%20his%20policies.%20The%20four%20prongs%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20and%20oratory%20are%20emotions%2C%20hyperbole%2C%20sarcasm%20and%20personal%20attacks%20on%20opponents.%20His%20modus%20operandi%20ensures%20that%20even%20emotional%20outbursts%20are%20planned%2C%20calibrated%20and%20targeted.%20Obversely%2C%20his%20silences%20are%20deafening%2C%20like%20his%20calculated%20quietude%20on%20Manipur.%20It%20took%20only%20a%20few%20months%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20prime%20minister%20is%20just%20too%20ruthlessly%20organised%20and%20his%20major%20skill%20lies%20in%20word-craft.%20The%20whisperati%20of%20Delhi%20spoke%20in%20hushed%20tones%20of%20how%20expensive%20professional%20advertising%20and%20marketing%20agencies%20were%20being%20tasked%20to%20produce%20%E2%80%9Ctaglines%20and%20gag%20lines%E2%80%9D.%20Every%20existing%20scheme%20or%20every%20%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(as%20Modi%20prefers%20to%20call%20welfare%20policies)%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fbjp-has-merely-renamed-19-out-of-23-congress-schemes-report%5C%22%3Erenamed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20prefixed%20with%20%E2%80%98Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99%2C%20after%20playing%20a%20lot%20of%20scrabble%20with%20each%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20obsession%20with%20self%20is%20only%20one%20essential%20component%20of%20%E2%80%98brand%20Modi%E2%80%99.%20He%20and%20his%20factotums%20put%20in%20all%20that%20they%20had%20to%20transform%20him%20from%20a%20leader%20to%20a%20trademark.%20His%20marketing%20campaign%2C%20run%20business-like%20by%20proficient%20agencies%2C%20ensured%20his%20name%20and%20face%20as%20%E2%80%98top%20of%20the%20mind%20recall%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrand%20Modi%20consists%20not%20only%20of%20changing%20one%E2%80%99s%20dress%20three%20times%20a%20single%20day%20but%20also%20of%20presenting%20hundreds%20of%20different%20faces%20throughout%20the%20last%20nine-and-a-quarter%20years.%20The%20shape%20and%20the%20grooming%20of%20his%20beard%20and%20hairstyle%20combine%20with%20thousand-odd%20costumes%20(this%20word%20is%20more%20apt%20than%20%E2%80%98clothes%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98dresses%E2%80%99)%20that%20he%20has%20adorned%20over%20the%20past%20112%20months.%20No%20one%20knows%20who%20pays%20for%20this%20splurge%20on%20the%20extravagant%20wardrobe%2C%20but%20what%20is%20more%20relevant%20is%20that%20the%20visage%20we%20accost%20is%20a%20carefully%20cultivated%20one%20%E2%80%93%20the%20one%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20desires%20to%20project.%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98candid%20camera%E2%80%99%20or%20a%20naturally%20dishevelled%20look%20is%20totally%20taboo.%20Photographers%20and%20the%20media%20know%20the%20consequences%20of%20publishing%20shots%20that%20reveal%20anything%20beyond%20the%20%E2%80%98authorised%E2%80%99%20image.%20His%20fondness%20for%20the%20Jawahar%20coat%20of%20every%20possible%20hue%2C%20despite%20the%20odious%20associations%20with%20its%20very%20name%2C%20has%20surely%20triggered%20several%20fashions%2C%20though%20his%20love%20for%20every%20conceivable%20headgear%20and%20%3Cem%3Eangavastram%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20met%20with%20similar%20success.%20His%20colleagues%20in%20the%20RSS%20mention%20that%20he%20would%20press%20his%20clothes%20every%20day%2C%20or%20have%20them%20ironed%2C%20for%20he%20would%20never%20be%20seen%20in%20any%20crushed%20apparel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06113659%2FF7hJGR7aoAAAdJJ.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06113659%2FF7hJGR7aoAAAdJJ.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06113659%2FF7hJGR7aoAAAdJJ-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06113659%2FF7hJGR7aoAAAdJJ-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678563%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Jagdalpur.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20four%20long%20decades%20as%20a%20bureaucrat%2C%20one%20has%20handled%20several%20%E2%80%98VVIP%20visits%E2%80%99%20but%20never%20has%20one%20come%20across%20such%20obsessive%20control%20over%20the%20camera.%20Everything%20is%20choreographed%20to%20give%20the%20best%20or%20the%20desired%20results%2C%20but%20this%20manipulation%20itself%20reveals%20certain%20painful%20inherent%20inadequacies%20that%20it%20seeks%20to%20hide%2C%20by%20projecting%20visuals%20that%20are%20basically%20%E2%80%98constructs%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20Modi%20is%20concerned%2C%20every%20facet%20of%20his%20presentation%20of%20himself%20is%20constructed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EEvery%20bit%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98accepted%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98official%E2%80%99%20biography%20is%20neatly%20arranged%20to%20bolster%20the%20desired%20version%20of%20reality.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20impudent%20keep%20asking%20embarrassing%20questions%20like%20in%20which%20school%20did%20he%20complete%20his%20secondary%20education%20or%20the%20name%20of%20the%20college%20of%20his%20graduation.%20Audacious%20ones%20even%20ask%20for%20his%20postgraduate%20degree%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelhi-university-authenticates-modis-ba-degree%5C%22%3Eentire%20political%20science%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99.%20Come%20to%20think%20of%20it%2C%20it%20is%20really%20odd%20that%20not%20a%20single%20high%20school%2C%20college%20or%20university%20teacher%20has%20come%20forward%20to%20say%20she%20or%20he%20taught%20Narendrabhai%20somewhere%2C%20nor%20do%20we%20have%20any%20person%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20studied%20in%20his%20class.%20Be%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20point%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20calculated%20projection%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20academic%20competence%20that%20is%20more%20important%20and%20real.%20He%20had%20the%20option%20of%20claiming%20that%20poverty%20and%20duty%20prevented%20his%20pursuit%20of%20studies%20beyond%20a%20point%2C%20but%20he%20was%20too%20enamoured%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98learned%20leader%E2%80%99%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbeyond-politics-caste-census-deepening-india-social-justice-paradigm%5C%22%3EBeyond%20Politics%3A%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20About%20Deepening%20India%E2%80%99s%20Social%20Justice%20Paradigm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20land%20of%20a%20billion%20poor%2C%20Modi%20has%20never%20hidden%20his%20humble%20origins%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20his%20penchant%20for%20Bvlgari%20glasses%2C%20Movado%20watches%2C%20Mont%20Blancs%20and%20Maybachs%2C%20which%20he%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20flaunted.%20He%20insisted%20that%20he%20was%20so%20poor%20a%20child%20that%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20tea%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefective-tea-kettle-dead-sabarmati%5C%22%3EVadnagar%20railway%20station%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20the%20knowledgeable%20insist%20that%20it%20was%20only%20a%20pass-through%20station%20during%20the%20entire%20period%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20and%20adolescence.%20The%20poor%20tea%20seller%20is%2C%20however%2C%20engraved%20into%20his%20self-representation%20and%20he%20repeated%20it%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20as%20well.%20Modi%20revels%20in%20this%20story%20as%20the%20only%20soft%20sentimental%20streak%20in%20a%20rock-hard%2C%20domineering%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20understand%20the%20boundless%20ambition%20of%20a%20man%20whose%20sheer%20ruthlessness%20overshadows%20apparent%20handicaps%20in%20his%20baggage.%20Early%20in%20his%20years%20in%20the%20RSS%2C%20he%20must%20have%20realised%20that%20he%20would%20find%20it%20impossible%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20seat%20of%20this%20incredibly%20powerful%20organisation.%20Brahmans%20had%20monopolised%20the%20post%20for%2092%20of%20its%2098%20years%20and%20a%20Rajput%20for%20the%20other%20six.%20Modi%20was%20neither.%20So%2C%20he%20moved%20on%20(or%20was%20deputed)%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20where%20his%20real%20rise%20took%20place%20after%20the%20bloodbath%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002.%20Even%20so%2C%20if%20he%20was%20to%20rule%20India%20with%20overwhelming%20numbers%2C%20he%20needed%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20that%20had%20the%20largest%20chunk%20%E2%80%93%20some%2040%25%20%E2%80%93%20of%20parliament%20seats.%20But%20he%20was%20not%20born%20in%20its%20zone.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98outlier%E2%80%99s%20obstinacy%E2%80%99%20set%20in.%20Greece%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20conqueror%2C%20Alexander%2C%20was%20not%20a%20Greek.%20He%20came%20from%20an%20adjacent%20but%20backward%20country%2C%20Macedonia.%20France%E2%80%99s%20mightiest%20emperor%2C%20Napoleon%2C%20was%20not%20from%20the%20mainland%20but%20from%20the%20wretched%20far-off%2C%20half-Italian%20island%20of%20Corsica.%20Hitler%20screamed%20about%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Third%20Reich%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20was%20an%20Austrian%2C%20not%20even%20a%20mainstream%20German.%20Yet%2C%20sheer%20grit%20and%20megalomania%20drove%20them%20to%20dizzy%20heights.%20Hence%2C%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Modi%20targeted%20and%20worked%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20for%20decades%2C%20acquiring%20mastery%20over%20language%2C%20accent%2C%20idiom%20and%20diction.%20Then%20when%20the%20big%20bell%20rang%2C%20the%20outlier%20struck%20his%20flag%20quite%20decisively%20at%20its%20very%20vortex%20of%20the%20mainstream%2C%20at%20Varanasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20just%20cannot%20let%20the%20opposition%20trample%20all%20over%20his%20carefully%20cultivated%20garden%2C%20by%20utilising%20the%20largest%20caste-group%2C%20the%20OBCs.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20realisation%20that%20%3Cspan%3Ecannot%20let%20the%20OBC%20vote%20bank%20slip%20out%20of%20his%20hands%20just%20because%20he%20did%20not%20use%20this%20identity%20till%20now%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ecomes%20quite%20late%20in%20the%20day.%20It%20may%20backfire%20as%20well.%20What%2C%20pray%2C%20did%20he%20do%20for%20the%20OBCs%20during%20his%20long%20reign%3F%20He%20even%20conjured%20a%2010%25%20for%20less-fortunate%20castes%20%E2%80%98above%E2%80%99%20the%20OBCs%2C%20and%20claimed%20to%20have%20fought%20for%20those%20%E2%80%98below%E2%80%99%20the%20OBCs%20as%20well.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20Brand%20Modi%20did%20not%20have%20any%20space%20for%20his%20OBC%20face%2C%20and%20may%20now%20find%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20sway%20the%20large%20chunk%20of%20OBC%20votes%20simply%20because%20he%20finds%20it%20convenient%20to%20highlight%20this%20identity%20once%20again%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20polls%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawhar-sircar%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawhar-sircar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EJawhar%20Sircar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20He%20has%20been%20culture%20secretary%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20CEO%20of%20Prasar%20Bharati.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696661746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmodi-obc-claim-identity-caste-census-social-justice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20four%20prongs%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20and%20oratory%20are%20emotions%2C%20hyperbole%2C%20sarcasm%20and%20p