hah%20recently%20discussed%20the%20importance%20of%20raising%20sons%20with%20the%20right%20values%2C%20drawing%20from%20her%20personal%20experience%20with%20street%20harassment%20as%20a%20young%20girl.%20She%20believes%20that%20the%20safety%20of%20daughters%20lies%20in%20the%20upbringing%20of%20sons%20and%20emphasizes%20treating%20others%20with%20respect.%20Shefali%2C%20having%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20International%20Emmy%20Awards%202023%20for%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20Crime%20Season%202%2C%26quot%3B%20expressed%20her%20elation.%20The%20series%2C%20directed%20by%20Tanuj%20Chopra%2C%20with%20Shefali%20in%20the%20lead%2C%20is%20inspired%20by%20real%20events%2C%20with%20its%20first%20season%20acclaimed%20for%20winning%20an%20International%20Emmy%20Award.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshefali-shah-recalls-the-horrors-of-street-harassment-when-she-was-young-claims-nobody-came-to-her-rescue%2Farticleshow%2F104232795.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20Will%20Inspire%20Women%20Around%20World%3A%20Telangana%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20leader%20Kalvakuntla%20Kavitha%20said%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20will%20inspire%20many%20women%20around%20the%20world%20to%20come%20forward%20in%20public%20life%20and%20called%20on%20women%20across%20continents%20to%20mobilise%20around%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20organised%20by%20the%20think%20tank%20Bridge%20India%20in%20London%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20the%20BRS%20Member%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20(MLC)%20addressed%20a%20diaspora%20audience%20at%20Central%20Hall%20Westminster%20near%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20%E2%80%98Gender%20Equality%20in%20India's%20Political%20Representation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20daughter%20of%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20virtually%20mobbed%20by%20the%20cheering%20diaspora%20crowds%2C%20highlighted%20the%20progress%20made%20in%20her%20own%20state%20that%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20nation%2C%20and%20we%20are%20about%2070%20crore%20women%3B%20if%20a%20very%20positive%20change%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20the%20women%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20I%20believe%20the%20world%20should%20know%20because%20that%20will%20inspire%20many%2C%20many%2C%20many%20more%20women%20to%20come%20forward%20in%20public%20life%2C%20to%20become%20active%20participants%20in%20policy%20making%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kavitha%20told%20PTI%20with%20reference%20to%20her%20London%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20received%20the%20Parliamentary%20nod%20on%20September%2021.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20gave%20her%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20on%20September%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20bill%2C%20I'm%20very%20confident%2C%20will%20enable%20that%20to%20happen%20to%20the%20women%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20India%2C%20and%20India's%20progress%20will%20see%20more%20and%20more%20participation%20of%20women%2C%20that%20is%20the%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2045-year-old%20politician%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20stronger%20representation%20of%20women%20within%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20country%2C%20she%20admitted%20that%20parties%20have%20traditionally%20been%20slow%20in%20addressing%20the%20matter%20satisfactorily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20say%20India%20is%20a%20much%20younger%20democracy%2C%20which%20is%2075%20years%20old.%20There%20are%20many%20democracies%20across%20the%20globe%20which%20are%20200%20years%20old%20or%20more%20who%20have%20still%20not%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20extent%20and%20level%20of%20women%20participation%20that%20we%20have%20reached%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20being%20said%2C%20the%20parties%20have%20to%20take%20the%20onus%20on%20themselves%20to%20make%20sure%20more%20and%20more%20women%20come%20in.%20And%20obviously%2C%20it's%20not%20happening%2C%20so%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20step%20in.%20It%20is%20for%20more%20laws%20to%20be%20put%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20the%20places%20for%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20charged%20address%20that%20drew%20applause%20and%20cheers%20from%20the%20crowd%2C%20Kavitha%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cpained%E2%80%9D%20her%20to%20state%20that%20inequality%20in%20public%20life%20is%20a%20reality%20around%20the%20world.%20She%20traced%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20that%20she%20had%20been%20campaigning%20for%20and%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20month%20%E2%80%93%20from%20former%20prime%20minister%20Deve%20Gowda%20in%201996%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20sincerely%20thank%20all%20of%20them%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20heart%20for%20making%20this%20bill%20a%20reality.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20politics%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20respect%20these%20people%20have%20shown%20to%20the%20women%20of%20this%20great%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20say%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20it%20is%20not%20only%20to%20make%20181%20women%20members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20but%20it%20is%20about%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20women.%20When%20we%20talk%20about%20women%2C%20countries%20don't%20matter%2C%20there%20are%20no%20borders.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9CAcross%20the%20globe%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20men%20managed%20to%20subjugate%20us%20for%20centuries.%20Now%2C%20the%20time%20has%20come%20that%20women%20across%20continents%20should%20connect%2C%20and%20should%20take%20up%20these%20issues.%20Today%2C%20if%20India%20has%20this%20bill%20and%20some%20other%20country%20does%20not%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20Indian%20women%20to%20go%20help%20our%20sisters%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20some%20light-hearted%20moments%20in%20her%20hard-hitting%20speech%2C%20she%20acknowledged%20her%20very%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20opinions%E2%80%9D%20and%20cautioned%20men%20to%20get%20used%20to%20hearing%20many%20more%20strong%20opinions%20from%20%E2%80%9Cour%20sisters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20referenced%20the%20Koh-i-Noor%20diamond%2C%20which%20has%20a%20connection%20to%20Telangana%2C%20given%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20Golconda%20mines.%20The%20MLC%20said%20while%20the%20discussion%20over%20the%20return%20of%20the%20infamous%20diamond%20to%20India%20will%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20on%20forever%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cat%20least%20give%20us%20back%20Vijay%20Mallya%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20referencing%20the%20former%20Kingfisher%20Airlines%20chief%20based%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20wanted%20in%20India%20on%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20Kavitha%20commenced%20her%20tour%20to%20the%20UK%20with%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20Ambedkar%20Museum%20in%20north%20London%20and%20spoke%20of%20how%20she%20drew%20great%20inspiration%20from%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20in%20her%20fight%20for%20gender%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMLC%20Kavitha's%20itinerary%20in%20the%20UK%20includes%20engagements%20with%20Indian%20diaspora%20groups%2C%20discussions%20on%20collaborative%20initiatives%20and%20participation%20in%20events%20to%20foster%20cultural%20exchange%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696660200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-09%2Ftrs-lead