Cspan%3EAnil%20Kumar%20and%20Ayush%20Ashna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20of%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%20died%20by%20suicide.%20Both%20students%2C%20barely%2020%20years%20old%2C%20belonged%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20Following%20these%20two%20deaths%20in%20the%20institution%2C%20the%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20(BSP)%2C%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20official%20media%20body%2C%20initiated%20a%20campus-based%20survey%20on%20caste%20discrimination.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20within%20a%20week%20as%20many%20students%20found%20it%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cirrelevant%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20about%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20similar%20survey%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20media%20body%20and%20the%20results%20are%20telling.%20The%20survey%20%E2%80%93%20based%20on%20545%20responses%20from%20undergraduate%20students%20%E2%80%93%20shows%20that%20two%20out%20of%20every%20three%20students%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98general%20category%E2%80%99%20felt%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstudents%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20reserved%20classes%20get%20undue%20advantages%20in%20IITD%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%98general%20category%E2%80%99%20consists%20mostly%20of%20students%20from%20savarna%20caste%20groups%20and%20some%20from%20religious%20minorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20from%20both%20savarna%20and%20Bahujan%20%E2%80%93%20those%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20%E2%80%93%20groups%20were%20surveyed.%20The%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20claims%20that%20permission%20was%20not%20given%20for%20the%20survey%20to%20be%20published%20on%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20hence%20the%20findings%20remained%20under%20wraps%20for%20close%20to%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20disturbing%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20shows%20that%20one%20in%20two%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20category%E2%80%9D%20respondents%20admitted%20to%20making%20casteist%20comments%20intentionally%20or%20unintentionally.%20Of%20them%2C%20nearly%2015%25%20admitted%20to%20having%20intentionally%20passed%20casteist%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20Bahujan%20students%2C%20the%20road%20to%20IITs%20was%20the%20first%20space%20where%20they%20encountered%20casteism.%20Over%2023%25%20of%20students%2C%20the%20survey%20said%2C%20faced%20casteism%20while%20preparing%20for%20JEE%2C%20the%20entrance%20exam%20for%20IITs.%20Over%2014%25%20of%20the%20participants%20shared%20that%20they%20encountered%20casteism%20after%20coming%20to%20IIT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20several%20cases%20of%20acute%20casteism%20and%20the%20deaths%20of%20students%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20communities%20due%20to%20institutional%20problems%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20at%20different%20IITs.%20While%20the%20institution%20has%20refused%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%20such%20surveys%20give%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20hostility%20and%20difficult%20environment%20that%20students%20have%20to%20navigate%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Finterview-merit-iit-caste-discrimination-vipin-veetilg%5C%22%3EInterview%20%7C%20%E2%80%98There%20Is%20Nothing%20Meritorious%20about%20IITs%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Prof%20Who%20Resigned%20Over%20Casteism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%2018-year-old%20IIT%20Bombay%20student%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiit-bombay-darshan-solanki-suicide%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDarshan%20Solanki%20died%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20university%20set%20up%20a%2012-member%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20death.%20The%20committee%20later%20came%20out%20with%20a%20controversial%20report%2C%20individualising%20his%20death%2C%20blaming%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20scores%E2%80%9D%20and%20completely%20disregarding%20the%20rampant%20casteism%20prevalent%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiit-bombay-suicide-did-authorities-fail-to-act-even-after-surveys-pointed-to-rampant-casteism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20different%20IIT%20Bombay%20bodies%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20the%20SC-ST%20student%20cell%2C%20had%20conducted%20multiple%20surveys%20towards%20the%20end%20of%202021.%20These%20brought%20out%20the%20insensitive%2C%20hostile%20and%20discriminatory%20atmosphere%20on%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IIT%20Delhi%20survey%20was%20also%20conducted%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20those%20conducted%20at%20its%20counterpart%20in%20Bombay%2C%20according%20to%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20campuses%2C%20like%20most%20other%20premier%20institutions%20in%20India%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20take%20corrective%20measures%20to%20change%20the%20environment%20on%20campus.%20Instead%2C%20as%20seen%20recently%2C%20IIT%20Bombay%20and%20IIT%20Hyderabad%20have%20set%20up%20segregated%20%E2%80%9Cvegetarian%20spaces%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20mess.%20A%20student%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cveg-only%20tables%E2%80%9D%20decision%20was%20fined%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT%20Bombay.%20Credit%3A%20University%20website%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-278024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIIT%20Bombay.%20Photo%3A%20University%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20shows%20that%2050%25%20of%20students%20from%20SC%2FST%20communities%20felt%20that%20students%20intentionally%20pass%20casteist%20comments.%20In%20the%20survey%2C%20when%20savarna%20students%20were%20asked%20questions%20about%20casteism%2C%20some%20claimed%20they%20faced%20%E2%80%9Ccasteist%20comments%E2%80%9D.%20This%2C%20the%20study%20says%2C%20shows%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdefinition%20mismatch%E2%80%9D%20among%20students%20belonging%20to%20different%20caste%20groups.%20This%20mismatch%2C%20research%20scholars%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20say%20comes%20from%20how%20students%20from%20different%20caste%20locations%20look%20at%20caste%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20savarna%20caste%20student%20will%20happily%20be%20a%20part%20of%20an%20anti-reservation%20WhatsApp%20group.%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20mind%20making%20casteist%20comments%20on%20the%20group.%20But%20if%20he%20finds%20out%20about%20a%20Bahujan%20student%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20an%20anti-caste%20social%20media%20group%2C%20he%20will%20cry%20hoarse%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20PhD%20student%20at%20IIT%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20research%20scholar%20pointed%20out%20some%20limitations%20of%20the%20survey.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20survey%20fails%20to%20recognise%20instances%20of%20%E2%80%98positive%20discrimination%E2%80%99.%20It%20groups%20terms%20used%20for%20marginalised%20groups%20and%20privileged%20groups%20as%20%E2%80%98casteism%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20assertions%20by%20those%20from%20marginalised%20identities%20too%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20casteist%20behavior%20%E2%80%93%20without%20understanding%20the%20context%20in%20which%20those%20statements%20were%20made%20or%20understood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20students%20but%20also%20professors%20and%20administrative%20staff%20who%20indulge%20in%20casteism%2C%20the%20survey%20claims%20%E2%80%93%2011%25%20of%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey%20claimed%20to%20know%20of%20%E2%80%9CIITD%20Professors%2Fadministrative%20staff%20who%20have%20made%20casteist%20comments%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20many%20face%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20are%20able%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20the%20survey%20indicates.%20Three%20out%20of%20four%20students%20from%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20categories%20are%20negatively%20affected%20by%20casteist%20comments%2C%20the%20survey%20finds.%20While%2059%25%20of%20the%20savarna%20students%20choose%20to%20remain%20neutral%20to%20the%20casteist%20atmosphere%2C%2041%25%20expressed%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnegatively%20impacted%E2%80%9D%20too.%20Of%20the%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20only%2020%25%20said%20they%20were%20able%20to%20oppose%20casteism%20when%20they%20encountered%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20savarna%20students%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%20against%20facilities%20made%20available%20to%20those%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20caste%20categories.%20Over%2060%25%20said%20they%20felt%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20unfair%E2%80%9D%20that%20people%20have%20to%20pay%20different%20fees%20based%20on%20their%20(caste)%20categories.%20Close%20to%2060%25%20found%20facilities%20like%20the%20book%20bank%20made%20available%20to%20students%20belonging%20to%20reserved%20categories%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20a%20similar%20questionnaire%20was%20sent%20out%20to%20students%20from%20across%20caste%20groups%2C%20the%20last%20question%20was%20visible%20only%20to%20those%20who%20filled%20OBC%2C%20SC%20or%20ST%20as%20their%20category.%20From%20these%20communities%2C%20215%20students%20responded.%20Of%20them%2C%2052%25%20belonged%20to%20OBC%20communities%20and%2048%25%20belonged%20to%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%2C%20the%20survey%20notes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20who%20responded%20to%20the%20last%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9C68%25%20of%20the%20reserved%20category%20respondents%20from%20metro%20cities%20felt%20that%20their%20achievements%20were%20undervalued%20as%20compared%20to%2024%25%20from%20a%20small%20village.%E2%80%9D%20A%20similar%20trend%2C%20the%20survey%20points%20out%2C%20can%20be%20observed%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20negatively%20affected%20when%20I%20hear%20a%20casteist%20comment%E2%80%9D%20option%20and%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20hesitant%20in%20disclosing%20my%20rank%2Fcaste%20in%20front%20of%20other%20people%20in%20my%20first%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20survey%20says%2088%25%20of%20the%20SC%20population%20and%2074%25%20of%20the%20ST%20population%20were%20hesitant%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20rank%20or%20caste%2C%20while%20the%20same%20is%20true%20for%2046%25%20of%20the%20OBC%20population.%20From%20the%20results%2C%20it%20can%20be%20inferred%2C%20the%20survey%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20students%20from%20the%20reserved%20categories%20feel%20undervalued%20and%20are%20negatively%20affected%20when%20someone%20makes%20a%20casteist%20comment%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696659946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F19152640%2FIIT_-_Delhi_-_Entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fiit-delhi-survey-glimpse-hostility-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20disturbing%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20shows%20that%20one%20in%20two%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20category%E2%80%9D%20respondents%20admitted%20to%20making%20casteist%20comments%20intentionally%20or%20unintentionally.%20Of%20them%2C%20nearly%2015%25%20admitted%20to%20having%20intentionally%20passed%20casteist%20comments.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fiit-delhi-survey-glimpse-hostility-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-lover%20of%20Spain's%20former%20king%20loses%20%24153%20million%20harassment%20lawsuit%20in%20London%20court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696659539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104232728%2Cimgsize-851266.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fex-lover-of-spains-former-king-loses-153-million-harassment-lawsuit-in-london-court%2Farticleshow%2F104232514.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104232514.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20Spanish%20King%20Juan%20Carlos%20I%20has%20won%20a%20court%20battle%20in%20London%20against%20his%20ex-lover%2C%20Corinna%20Larsen.%20Larsen%2C%20a%20Danish%20socialite%2C%20had%20sought%20%C2%A3126%20million%20in%20damages%2C%20claiming%20that%20she%20was%20harassed%20and%20spied%20on%20by%20Juan%20Carlos%20after%20their%20breakup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi