ble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20heavy%20fighting%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20and%20nearly%20200%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20military%20raids%20this%20year.%20Israel%20says%20the%20raids%20are%20aimed%20at%20militants%2C%20but%20stone-throwing%20protesters%20and%20people%20uninvolved%20in%20the%20violence%20have%20also%20been%20killed.%20Palestinian%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20targets%20have%20killed%20over%2030%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECasualties%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20towns%20of%20Ashkelon%2C%20Gedera%20and%20Yavne.%20A%2070-year-old%20woman%20was%20critically%20injured%20when%20a%20rocket%20directly%20hit%20a%20building%20near%20Gedera%2C%20the%20Magen%20David%20Adom%20ambulance%20service%20said.%20Fifteen%20others%20were%20hurt%2C%20two%20of%20them%20seriously%2C%20medics%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20is%20expected%20to%20hold%20consultations%20with%20top%20defence%20officials%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20DPA%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-says-militants-infiltrated-from-gaza%2Fa-67025942%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp