ople%20at%20a%20rally%20whether%20he%20should%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20again%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20political%20circles%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20abuzz%20with%20speculation%20about%20Shivraj%20Chouhan's%20return%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20several%20stalwarts%20as%20its%20candidates%2C%20who%20may%20be%20considered%20as%20contenders%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%20if%20the%20party%20retains%20power%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Dindori%20on%20Friday%2C%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20asked%20people%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ask%20you%20whether%20I%20am%20running%20a%20good%20government%20or%20a%20bad%20government.%20So%2C%20should%20this%20government%20move%20ahead%20or%20not%3F%20Should%20Mama%20(as%20he%20is%20popularly%20called)%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20not%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20them%20if%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20country's%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20whether%20the%20BJP%20should%20retain%20power%20(in%20the%20state%20and%20centre).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attendees%20replied%20to%20both%20the%20questions%20in%20the%20affirmative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Dhar%20district%20of%20the%20state%20on%20Thursday%2C%20claimed%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20will%20not%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20ji%20comes%20here...Nowadays%20he%20is%20shying%20away%20from%20mentioning%20the%20name%20of%20Shivraj%20ji...%20just%20taking%20his%20own%20name%20and%20asking%20(people)%20to%20vote%20for%20me%20(Narendra%20Modi).%20Now%20he%20(Shivraj%20Chouhan)%20is%20not%20going%20to%20become%20your%20CM%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi-Vadra%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShivraj%20Chouhan%2C%20the%20state's%20longest%20serving%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20seen%20getting%20emotional%20during%20public%20events%20and%20rallies%20recently.%20In%20a%20public%20event%20held%20in%20his%20home-turf%20Budhni%20held%20recently%2C%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20asked%20people%20if%20he%20should%20contest%20elections%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20Budhni%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20told%20women%20that%20they%20would%20miss%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrother%20like%20me%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20is%20not%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20held%20in%20Ujjain%20on%20Friday%2C%20he%20said%20the%20path%20of%20politics%20was%20slippery%20and%20there%20was%20fear%20of%20slipping%20at%20every%20step%2C%20and%20sought%20the%20blessings%20of%20spiritual%20leaders%20attending%20the%20event%20to%20ensure%20he%20continues%20to%20%26quot%3Bwalk%20on%20the%20path%20of%20virtue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20Khargone%2C%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20had%20said%20he%20had%20no%20greed%20for%20any%20post%20and%20that%20he%20would%20be%20happy%20even%20if%20his%20bones%20and%20flesh%20come%20of%20use%20and%20do%20good%20to%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20recent%20statements%20seeking%20public%20permission%20about%20his%20candidature%20during%20the%20upcoming%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20on%20Friday%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20we%20consider%20(each%20other)%20brother%20and%20sisters.%20Mama's%20family%2C%20which%20is%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20understands%20this.%20If%20we%20have%20to%20contest%20(elections)%2C%20then%20we%20will%20do%20this%20only%20after%20asking%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20family%20relation%20and%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20insight%20to%20understand%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElections%20to%20the%20230-member%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20announced%20the%20names%20of%2079%20candidates%2C%20who%20include%20Union%20ministers%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Prahlad%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%2C%20as%20well%20as%20party's%20senior%20leader%20and%20Indore%20strongman%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20all%20political%20heavyweights%20being%20seen%20as%20contenders%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Mr%20Vijayvargiya%20said%20he%20was%20contesting%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20not%20only%20to%20become%20an%20MLA%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20party%20would%20give%20him%20some%20important%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20August%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20Mr%20Chouhan%20would%20be%20Chief%20Ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20party%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20and%20BJP's%20key%20strategist%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20counter-questioned%20the%20media%20asking%20why%20it%20was%20doing%20the%20%26quot%3Bparty's%20work%20(choosing%20persons%20for%20posts)%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696659240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8v7o0plo_shivraj-singh-chauhan_625x300_08_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshould-i-be-chief-minister-again-shivraj-chouhan-at-madhya-pradesh-rally-4458333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20wake%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20predicting%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh's%20Chouhan's%20exit%20from%20the%20top%20post%2C%20the%20latter%20asked%20people%20at%20a%20rally%20whether%20he%20should%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%