r-ferrari-accident-who-is-realtor-vikas-oberoi-involved-in-horrific-lamborghini-ferrari-crash-in-italy-4448355%5C%22%3EVikas%20Oberoi%3C%2Fa%3E%20returned%20to%20Mumbai%20just%20days%20after%20they%20escaped%20unhurt%20in%20a%20horrific%20car%20crash%20in%20Italy%20involving%20their%20Lamborghini%20and%20a%20Ferrari.%20Two%20people%20had%20died%20in%20the%20accident%20that%20occurred%20on%20October%202%20in%20Italy's%20Sardinia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVikas%20Oberoi%2C%20a%20billionaire%20is%20the%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Oberoi%20Realty%2C%20a%20developer%20of%20luxury%20and%20premium%20homes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgayatri-joshi-gayatri-joshi-swades-video-shows-moment-actor-gayatri-joshis-lamborghini-crashed-into-ferrari-4451190%5C%22%3EGayatri%20Joshi%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20her%20Bollywood%20debut%20alongside%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan-starrer%20%E2%80%98Swades'%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Oberoi%20group%20in%20a%20statement%20announced%20that%20the%20couple%20was%20safe%20and%20had%20returned%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20Mr%20Vikas%20Oberoi%20and%20his%20wife%20Mrs%20Gayatri%20Oberoi%20were%20in%20a%20multiple%20car%20accident%20in%20Sardinia%2C%20Italy%20early%20this%20week.%20They%20are%20safe%20and%20have%20returned%20to%20Mumbai%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Realty%20Group%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Italian%20media%20reports%2C%20police%20have%20not%20registered%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20against%2054-year-old%20Vikas%20Oberoi.%20The%20reports%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20police%20have%20obtained%20a%20number%20of%20videos%20from%20the%20crash%20site%20and%20are%20investigating%20each%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20took%20place%20during%20the%20Sardinia%20Supercar%20Tour%2C%20which%20features%20a%20luxury%20car%20parade%20from%20Teulada%20to%20Olbia%20that%20lets%20drivers%20explore%20the%20area%