n%20Pfetcher%2C%20seeks%20to%20%E2%80%9Cset%20the%20record%20straight%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20investment.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20arrested%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20portal%E2%80%99s%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3Eaccusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20of%20using%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amount%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chinese%20funding%20to%20publish%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20news%E2%80%9D%20which%20criticised%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20promote%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPfetcher%20said%20that%20all%20of%20the%20funds%20of%20WMH%2C%20which%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Support%20Foundation%2C%20came%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20US%20businessman%20Neville%20Singham%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20company%20ThoughtWorks%20and%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20received%20funds%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWMH%E2%80%99s%20investment%20in%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20finalised%20in%20March%202018%2C%20Pfetcher%20said.%20Reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20investment%20%E2%80%9Cstrictly%20followed%20all%20aspects%20of%20Indian%20law%2C%20specifically%20including%20those%20limiting%20foreign%20ownership%20in%20media%20companies%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20has%20attended%20various%20shareholder%20meetings%20on%20behalf%20of%20WMH%20but%20nobody%20linked%20to%20the%20for-profit%20company%20has%20%E2%80%9Cever%20influenced%2C%20guided%2C%20or%20directed%20the%20journalistic%20work%E2%80%9D%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFalse%20allegations%20about%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20continue%20to%20circulate%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20facts%20WMH%20has%20given%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20These%20dire%20circumstances%20compel%20me%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20that%20was%20published%20in%20August%2C%20accusing%20Roy%20Singham%20of%20spreading%20Chinese%20propaganda%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20before%20the%20article%20was%20published%2C%20he%20issued%20a%20statement%20which%20said%20the%20company%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20received%20any%20funding%2C%20nor%20taken%20direction%20from%20any%20foreign%20individual%2C%20organization%2C%20political%20party%2C%20or%20government%20(or%20from%20any%20of%20their%20members%20or%20representatives)%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20to%20include%E2%80%9D%20and%20instead%20left%20readers%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20source%20of%20Roy%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20funding%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20have%20come%20from%20China%2C%20rather%20than%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20salacious%20headlines%20and%20misleading%20%E2%80%98reporting%E2%80%99%20have%20now%20directly%20contributed%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20innocent%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pfetcher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20repression%20that%20is%20now%20taking%20place%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20India%20is%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20foreign%20investors%20who%20carefully%20follow%20Indian%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20name%20is%20Jason%20Pfetcher.%20I%20am%20a%20lawyer%20based%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%20regarding%20Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20LLC%20(%E2%80%9CWMH%E2%80%9D)%20and%20an%20investment%20made%20by%20WMH%20to%20PPK%20Newsclick%20Studio%20Private%20Limited%20(%E2%80%9CNewsclick%E2%80%9D)%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20an%20attorney%20in%20the%20United%20States%20for%20over%2025%20years.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20ThoughWorks%2C%20Inc.%2C%20an%20IT%20consultancy%20that%20has%20a%20worldwide%20footprint.%20I%20left%20ThoughtWorks%20in%202017%20when%20the%20company%20was%20sold%20to%20a%20British%20private%20equity%20fund%2C%20Apax%20Partners%20(founded%20in%201969).%20I%20joined%20ThoughtWorks%E2%80%99%20founder%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20(%E2%80%9CRoy%E2%80%9D)%2C%20to%20assist%20him%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20give%20away%20most%20of%20the%20proceeds%20he%20received%20from%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20created%20a%20private%20foundation%20in%20the%20United%20States%20called%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Support%20Foundation%2C%20Limited%20(%E2%80%9CPSF%E2%80%9D)%2C%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20board%20member%20since%20its%20inception.%20All%20funds%20donated%20to%20PSF%20came%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks.%20PSF%20has%20never%20received%20funds%20from%20a%20foreign%20government.%20PSF%20wholly%20owns%20and%20operates%20WMH%2C%20of%20which%20I%20am%20the%20manager.%20WMH%20is%20a%20for-profit%20investment%20vehicle%20which%20has%20made%20various%20investments%20in%20progressive%20media%20projects%20around%20the%20world%20that%20provide%20people-centered%20news%20coverage.%20While%20these%20entities%20are%20consistent%20with%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20PSF%20seeks%20a%20return%20on%20the%20investments%20we%20make%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%202017%2C%20WMH%20identified%20Newsclick%20as%20an%20organization%20that%20was%20consistent%20with%20WMH%E2%80%99s%20purposes%20and%20commenced%20due%20diligence%20on%20a%20potential%20investment%20in%20Newsclick.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20I%20visited%20Delhi%20and%20hired%20local%20counsel%2C%20met%20with%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20editor%20and%20other%20Newsclick%20staff%2C%20toured%20its%20facilities%2C%20and%20negotiated%20with%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20legal%20counsel.%20Following%20the%20completion%20of%20due%20diligence%2C%20the%20PSF%20board%20determined%20that%20it%20was%20advisable%20that%20WMH%20invest%20in%20Newsclick.%20That%20investment%20was%20finalized%20in%20March%202018.%20While%20I%20have%20attended%20various%20shareholder%20meetings%20of%20Newsclick%20on%20behalf%20of%20WMH%2C%20none%20of%20the%20principals%20of%20PSF%20or%20WMH%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20have%20ever%20influenced%2C%20guided%2C%20or%20directed%20the%20journalistic%20work%20of%20Newsclick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Newsclick%20investment%20opportunity%20came%20to%20WMH%2C%20in%20part%2C%20from%20our%20relationship%20with%20Prabir%20Purkayastha.%20I%20met%20Prabir%20while%20working%20at%20ThoughtWorks%3B%20we%20were%20fellow%20employees%20there%20for%20many%20years.%20Prabir%20was%2C%20and%20remains%2C%20highly%20regarded%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20technologist%2C%20scientist%2C%20researcher%2C%20and%20business%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20offices%20were%20raided%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20which%20accused%20the%20organization%20of%20money%20laundering.%20The%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20subsequently%20initiated%20its%20own%20investigation%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Revenue%20Service%20of%20India.%20Over%20many%20months%2C%20dozens%20of%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20journalists%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20other%20associates%2C%20including%20Prabir%20and%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20were%20interrogated%20at%20length%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20WMH%20has%20provided%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20confirmation%20regarding%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20by%20WMH.%20WMH%20has%20also%20provided%20ample%20evidence%20that%20it%20is%20and%20has%20always%20been%20in%20good%20standing%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Delaware%20where%20it%20is%20incorporated%2C%20despite%20false%20information%20being%20circulated%20that%20WMH%20was%20a%20defunct%20entity%20when%20it%20invested%20in%20Newsclick.%20Prabir%2C%20along%20with%20Amit%2C%20have%20now%20been%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20offices%20have%20been%20sealed.%20False%20allegations%20about%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20continue%20to%20circulate%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20facts%20WMH%20has%20given%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20These%20dire%20circumstances%20compel%20me%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20much%20of%20the%20basis%20for%20this%20action%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20stems%20from%20a%20slanderous%20article%20that%20was%20published%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20on%20August%205%2C%202023.%20Before%20that%20article%20was%20published%2C%20I%20responded%20to%20the%20reporters%E2%80%99%20questions%20on%20behalf%20of%20PSF%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CPSF%20has%20never%20received%20any%20funding%2C%20nor%20taken%20direction%20from%20any%20foreign%20individual%2C%20organization%2C%20political%20party%2C%20or%20government%20(or%20from%20any%20of%20their%20members%20or%20representatives).%E2%80%9D%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20failed%20to%20include%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20categorical%20denial%20of%20foreign%20funding%2C%20and%20instead%20left%20readers%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20source%20of%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20funding%20(or%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20for%20that%20matter)%20might%20have%20come%20from%20China%2C%20rather%20than%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks.%20Their%20salacious%20headlines%20and%20misleading%20%E2%80%98reporting%E2%80%99%20have%20now%20directly%20contributed%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20innocent%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20traveling%20to%20India%20and%20doing%20business%20there%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%20I%20recommended%20this%20particular%20investment%20without%20hesitation%2C%20eager%20to%20see%20India%E2%80%99s%20already%20vibrant%20media%20landscape%20be%20made%20even%20more%20so%20by%20the%20growth%20of%20a%20media%20project%20eager%20to%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20voiceless.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20highly%20conscientious%20about%20respecting%20local%20laws.%20Therefore%2C%20reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20investment%20strictly%20followed%20all%20aspects%20of%20Indian%20law%2C%20specifically%20including%20those%20limiting%20foreign%20ownership%20in%20media%20companies.%20Given%20the%20repression%20that%20is%20now%20taking%20place%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20India%20is%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20foreign%20investors%20who%20carefully%20follow%20Indian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696656520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07105239%2F5mtb93eo_neville-roy-singham-1200_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-case-no-foreign-funding-neville-roy-singham-company-statement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20said%20that%20reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20investment%20%26quot%3Bstrictly%20followed%20all%20aspects%20of%20Indian%20law%2C%20specifically%20including%20those%20limiting%20foreign%20ownership%20in%20media%20companies%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-case-no-foreign-funding-neville-roy-singham-company-statement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian%20gunmen%20reported%20in%20Israel%20as%20barrages%20launched%20from%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%