militant%20group%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthousands-of-rockets-fired-into-israel-as-video-shows-palestinian-fighters-crossing-border-on-paragliders-12978797%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthousands-of-rockets-fired-into-israel-as-video-shows-palestinian-fighters-crossing-border-on-paragliders-12978797%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthousands-of-rockets-fired-into-israel-as-video-shows-palestinian-fighters-crossing-border-on-paragliders-12978797%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dozens%20Of%20Rockets%20Fired%20From%20Gaza%20Towards%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20rockets%20were%20fired%20from%20the%20blockaded%20Gaza%20Strip%20towards%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%2C%20an%20AFP%20journalist%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20said%2C%20as%20sirens%20warning%20of%20incoming%20fire%20blared%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%20fire%20was%20launched%20from%20multiple%20locations%20in%20Gaza%20starting%20at%2006%3A30%20am%20(0330%20GMT)%2C%20the%20AFP%20journalist%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20warned%20of%20sirens%20across%20the%20country's%20south%20and%20central%20areas%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20urging%20the%20public%20to%20stay%20near%20bomb%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20number%20of%20terrorists%20have%20infiltrated%20into%20Israeli%20territory%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20providing%20further%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2070-year-old%20woman%20was%20in%20critical%20condition%20and%20another%20person%20was%20trapped%20after%20a%20rocket%20hit%20a%20building%20in%20central%20Israel%2C%20the%20Magen%20David%20Adom%20emergency%20services%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20incident%2C%20medics%20sai