ed%20the%20team's%20vehicle%20and%20held%20them%20hostage%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20government%20provide%20them%20with%20a%20subsidy%20for%20purchasing%20straw%20management%20machines.%20They%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20government%20increase%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20paddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-delhi-air-quality-poor-again-diwali-still-a-month-away-4458356%5C%22%3EPlan%20To%20Control%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Kicks%20In%20Day%20After%20Air%20Quality%20Turns%20Poor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20were%20eventually%20released%20after%20the%20intervention%20of%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20district%20administration%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20governments%20are%20cracking%20down%20on%20stubble%20burning%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ordered%20action%20against%20farmers%20who%20burn%20stubble%2C%20but%20the%20farmers%20say%20that%20burning%20crop%20residue%20benefits%20them%20and%20increases%20crop%20yields.%20They%20have%20warned%20the%20administration%20that%20they%20will%20take%20hostage%20any%20administrative%20representative%20who%20comes%20to%20rural%20areas%20to%20issue%20challans%2C%20and%20that%20they%20will%20launch%20a%20large-scale%20agitation%20if%20any%20farmer%20is%20charged%20during%20this%20time.%20The%20farmers%20recently%20protested%20at%20the%20Ambala%20Mini%20Secretariat%20to%20make%20their%20demands%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgriculture%20officials%20are%20educating%20farmers%20about%20the%20issue.%20But%20despite%20appeals%20from%20the%20administration%2C%20farmers%20in%20Ambala%20are%20burning%20crop%20residue%20as%20they%20prepare%20their%20fields%20for%20the%20next%20crop%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20no%20other%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambala%20Agriculture%20Department%20has%20issued%20challans%20to%20many%20farmers%20for%20burning%20stubble%2C%20and%20is%20investigating%20many%20cases.%20The%20farmers%20are%20protesting%20against%20this%20action%2C%20but%20the%20department%20says%20it%20is%20raising%20awareness%20among%20farmers%20and%20many%20are%20now%20complying%20with%20the%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStubble%20burning%20in%20Punjab%20has%20increased%20significantly%20this%20year%2C%20with%20656%20farm%20fire%20incidents%20reported%20from%20September%2015%20to%20October%204%2C%20compared%20to%20415%20and%20260%20in%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022%20and%202021%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696654440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ffbed8tno_haryana-officials-held-hostage-by-farmers-_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fout-to-inspect-stubble-burning-haryana-officials-held-hostage-by-farmers-4458432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20three%20government%20officials%20was%20allegedly%20held%20hostage%20by%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20in%20Haryana's%20Ambala%20district%20on%20Thursday%20when%20they%20were%20on%20patrol%20to%20check%20stubble%20burning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fout-to-inspect-stubble-burning-haryana-officials-held-hostage-by-farmers-4458432%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fout-to-inspect-stubble-burning-haryana-officials-held-h