028.%20His%20groundbreaking%20contributions%20to%20agriculture%20revolutionised%20food%20security%20in%20India%20and%20had%20earned%20him%20global%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20PM's%20blog%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProf.%20Swaminathan's%20unyielding%20commitment%20and%20foresight%20ushered%20a%20new%20era%20of%20agricultural%20prosperity%3A%20PM%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%20we%20lost%20Professor%20M.S.%20Swaminathan.%20Our%20nation%20lost%20a%20visionary%20who%20revolutionised%20agricultural%20science%2C%20a%20stalwart%20whose%20contribution%20to%20India%20will%20always%20be%20etched%20in%20golden%20letters.%20Prof.%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20loved%20India%20and%20wanted%20our%20nation%2C%20and%20our%20farmers%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20of%20prosperity.%20Academically%20brilliant%2C%20he%20could%20have%20chosen%20any%20career%20but%20he%20was%20so%20impacted%20by%20the%20Bengal%20famine%20of%201943%20that%20he%20was%20clear%20that%20if%20there%20is%20one%20thing%20he%20would%20do%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20study%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20relatively%20young%20age%2C%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Dr.%20Norman%20Borlaug%20and%20followed%20his%20work%20in%20great%20detail.%20In%20the%201950's%2C%20he%20was%20offered%20a%20faculty%20position%20in%20the%20US%20but%20he%20rejected%20it%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20India%20and%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20want%20you%20all%20to%20think%20about%20the%20challenging%20circumstances%20in%20which%20he%20stood%20as%20a%20colossus%2C%20guiding%20our%20nation%20towards%20the%20path%20of%20self-sufficiency%20and%20self-confidence.%20In%20the%20first%20two%20decades%20since%20Independence%2C%20we%20were%20dealing%20with%20immense%20challenges%20and%20one%20of%20them%20was%20food%20shortages.%20In%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20India%20was%20grappling%20with%20the%20ominous%20shadows%20of%20famine%20and%20it%20is%20then%20that%20Prof.%20Swaminathan's%20unyielding%20commitment%20and%20foresight%20ushered%20a%20new%20era%20of%20agricultural%20prosperity.%20His%20pioneering%20work%20in%20agriculture%20and%20specific%20sectors%20like%20wheat%20breeding%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20wheat%20production%2C%20thus%20turning%20India%20from%20a%20food-deficient%20country%20into%20a%20self-sufficient%20nation.%20This%20tremendous%20achievement%20earned%20him%20the%20well%20deserved%20title%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BFather%20of%20the%20Indian%20Green%20Revolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Green%20Revolution%20offered%20a%20glimpse%20of%20India's%20%26quot%3BCan%20Do%20Spirit%26quot%3B%20-%20that%20if%20we%20have%20a%20billion%20challenges%2C%20we%20also%20have%20a%20billion%20minds%20with%20the%20flame%20of%20innovation%20to%20overcome%20those%20challenges.%20Five%20decades%20after%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20began%2C%20Indian%20agriculture%20has%20become%20far%20more%20modern%20and%20progressive.%20But%2C%20the%20very%20foundations%20laid%20by%20Prof.%20Swaminathan%20can%20never%20be%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20he%20undertook%20pioneering%20research%20in%20combatting%20parasites%20affecting%20potato%20crops.%20His%20research%20also%20enabled%20potato%20crops%20to%20withstand%20cold%20weather.%20Today%2C%20the%20world%20is%20talking%20about%20Millets%20or%20Shree%20Anna%20as%20super%20foods%20but%20Prof.%20Swaminathan%20had%20encouraged%20discourse%20around%20millets%20since%20the%201990's.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20personal%20interactions%20with%20Prof.%20Swaminathan%20were%20extensive.%20They%20began%20after%20I%20took%20over%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%20in%202001.%20During%20those%20days%2C%20Gujarat%20was%20not%20known%20for%20its%20agricultural%20prowess.%20Successive%20droughts%20and%20a%20super%20cyclone%20and%20an%20Earthquake%20had%20impacted%20the%20growth%20trajectory%20of%20the%20state.%20Among%20the%20many%20initiatives%20we%20launched%2C%20was%20the%20Soil%20Health%20Card%2C%20which%20enabled%20us%20to%20understand%20the%20soil%20better%20and%20address%20problems%20if%20they%20arose.%20It%20was%20in%20the%20context%20of%20this%20scheme%20that%20I%20met%20Prof.%20Swaminathan.%20He%20appreciated%20the%20scheme%20and%20also%20shared%20his%20valuable%20inputs%20for%20the%20same.%20His%20endorsement%20was%20enough%20to%20convince%20those%20who%20were%20sceptical%20about%20the%20scheme%20which%20would%20eventually%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20Gujarat's%20agricultural%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20interactions%20continued%20during%20my%20Chief%20Ministerial%20tenure%20and%20also%20when%20I%20took%20over%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20I%20met%20him%20at%20the%20International%20Agro-Biodiversity%20Congress%20in%202016%20and%20the%20next%20year%20in%202017%2C%20I%20launched%20a%20two-part%20book%20series%20written%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kural%20describes%20farmers%20as%20the%20pin%20that%20holds%20the%20world%20together%20because%20it%20is%20the%20farmers%20who%20sustain%20everyone.%20Prof.%20Swaminathan%20understood%20this%20principle%20very%20well.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20call%20him%20a%20%26quot%3BKrishi%20Vaigyanik%26quot%3B%20-%20an%20Agricultural%20Scientist.%20But%2C%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20he%20was%20even%20more.%20He%20was%20a%20true%20%26quot%3BKisan%20Vaigyanik%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20Farmers'%20Scientist.%20In%20his%20heart%20there%20was%20a%20farmer.%20The%20success%20of%20his%20works%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20their%20academic%20excellence%3B%20it%20lies%20in%20the%20impact%20they%20have%20had%20outside%20the%20laboratories%2C%20in%20the%20farms%20and%20the%20fields.%20His%20work%20narrowed%20the%20gap%20between%20scientific%20knowledge%20and%20its%20practical%20application.%20He%20consistently%20advocated%20for%20sustainable%20agriculture%2C%20emphasising%20the%20delicate%20balance%20between%20human%20advancement%20and%20ecological%20sustainability.%20Here%2C%20I%20must%20also%20note%20Prof.%20Swaminathan's%20special%20emphasis%20on%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20small%20farmers%20and%20ensuring%20they%20also%20enjoy%20the%20fruits%20of%20innovation.%20He%20was%20particularly%20passionate%20about%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20women%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20aspect%20about%20Prof.%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20which%20is%20remarkable%20-%20he%20stands%20tall%20as%20a%20paragon%20of%20innovation%20and%20mentorship.%20When%20he%20won%20the%20World%20Food%20Prize%20in%201987%2C%20the%20first%20recipient%20of%20this%20prestigious%20honour%2C%20he%20used%20the%20prize%20money%20to%20establish%20a%20not-for-profit%20research%20foundation.%20Till%20date%2C%20it%20undertakes%20extensive%20work%20across%20various%20sectors.%20He%20has%20nurtured%20countless%20minds%2C%20instilling%20in%20them%20a%20passion%20for%20learning%20and%20innovation.%20In%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20world%2C%20his%20life%20reminds%20us%20of%20the%20enduring%20power%20of%20knowledge%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20innovation.%20He%20was%20an%20institution%20builder%20as%20well%2C%20having%20to%20his%20credit%20many%20centres%20where%20vibrant%20research%20takes%20place.%20One%20of%20his%20stints%20was%20as%20Director%2C%20International%20Rice%20Research%20Institute%2C%20Manila.%20The%20South%20Asia%20Regional%20Centre%20of%20International%20Rice%20Research%20Institute%20was%20opened%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20will%20again%20cite%20The%20Kural%20to%20pay%20tributes%20to%20Dr.%20Swaminathan.%20It%20is%20written%20there%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20those%20who%20have%20planned%20have%20firmness%2C%20they%20will%20attain%20what%20they%20have%20desired%20the%20way%20they%20have%20desired.%26quot%3B%20Here%20was%20a%20stalwart%20who%20decided%20early%20on%20in%20his%20life%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20strengthen%20agriculture%20and%20serve%20farmers.%20And%2C%20he%20did%20it%20exceptionally%20innovatively%20and%20passionately.%20Dr.%20Swaminathan's%20contributions%20continue%20to%20inspire%20and%20guide%20us%20as%20we%20navigate%20the%20path%20of%20agricultural%20innovation%20and%20sustainability.%20We%20must%20also%20keep%20reaffirming%20our%20commitment%20to%20the%20principles%20he%20held%20dear%2C%20championing%20the%20cause%20of%20farmers%20and%20ensuring%20the%20fruits%20of%20scientific%20innovation%20reach%20the%20roots%20of%20our%20agricultural%20expanse%2C%20fostering%20growth%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20prosperity%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696653480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fben6bsm_modi-ms-swaminathan_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-true-farmers-scientist-pm-narendra-modi-praises-ms-swaminathan-in-latest-blog-4458401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Swaminathan's%20unyielding%20commitment%20and%20foresight%20ushered%20a%20new%20era%20of%20agricultural%20prosperity%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wrote%20in%20his%20latest%20blog%20onnarendramodi.in%2C%20days%20after%20the%20death%20of%20the%20renowned%20agricultural%20scientist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-true-farmers-scientist-pm-narendra-modi-praises-ms-swaminathan-in-latest-blog-4458401%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-true-farmers-scientist-pm-narendra-modi-praises-ms-swaminathan-in-latest-blog-4458401%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-true-farmers-scientist-pm-narendra-modi-praises-ms-swaminathan-in-latest-blog-4458401%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKya%20Julm%20Hai...%26quot%3B%20Veep%20Jabs%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20For%20Questioning%20Rajasthan%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20questioned%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20over%20his%20frequent%20visits%20to%20the%20poll-bound%20state%2C%20the%20latter%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20drag%20a%20person%20holding%20a%20constitutional%20post%20unnecessarily%20into%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20reply%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20that%20there%20must%20be%20respect%20for%20constitutional%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20saying%20why%20are%20you%20coming%20here%20again%20and%20again...%20I%20do%20not%20expect%2C%20people%20in%20authority%20to%20make%20statements%20in%20light%20of%20constitutional%20positions.%20This%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy.%20There%20must%20be%20respect%20for%20constitutional%20positions%20and%20all%20of%20us%20in%20togetherness%2C%20hand%20in%20hand%2C%20in%20collaboration%20and%20coordination%20with%20a%20consensual%20approach%2C%20have%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20at%20large...%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice%20President%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20students%20and%20faculty%20members%20of%20Mody%20University%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20in%20Laxmangarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20lashed%20out%20at%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20on%20several%20occasions%20over%20his%20frequent%20visits%20to%20the%20poll-bound%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20country%2C%20we%20all%20are%20servants%20of%20this%20country%20whatever%20be%20our%20position%2C%20right%20from%20the%20President%20down%20the%20line%20up%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%20We%20must%20be%20very%20sensitive%2C%20we%20should%20not%20generate%20such%20a%20public%20perception%20that%20a%20person%20holding%20a%20constitutional%20post%20should%20be%20unnecessarily%20dragged%20into%20politics%2C%20it%20is%20not%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20also%20recited%20a%20poem%20written%20by%20him%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BKhata%20kya%20ki%20humne%2C%20pata%20hi%20nahi!%20Aapatti%20kyo%20hai%20unhe%20hamare%20ghar%20aane%20ki%2C%20pata%20hi%20nahi!%20Ye%20kaisa%20manzar%20hai%2C%20samjh%20se%20pare%20hai%2C%20Sawaliya%20nishan%20kyo%20hai%20apne%20ghar%20aane%20me%2C%20Kya%20julm%20hai%3F%20Pata%20hi%20nahi!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20poem%20refers%20to%20someone%20having%20a%20problem%20with%20him%20going%20to%20their%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20programme%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20Mr%20Gehlot%20had%20said%20in%20September%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Vice%20President%20is%20doing%20up-down%20(between%20Delhi%20and%20Rajasthan).%20Whether%20it%20is%20the%20Governor%20or%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%20we%20respect%20them...%20but%20elections%20are%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoliticians%20should%20come%20but%20please%20do%20not%20send%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Constitutional%20post.%20We%20respect%20the%20President%20and%20the%20Vice%20President.%20Yesterday%20the%20Vice%20President%20came%20and%20visited%20five%20districts.%20Is%20there%20any%20logic%3F%20It%20is%20election%20season.%20If%20you%20come%20now%20it%20will%20send%20all%20kinds%20of%20messages%20which%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696653360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F2lhsm0hg_jagdeep-dhankhar-pti_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvice-president-turns-poet-to-counter-ashok-gehlots-objections-to-visits-4457206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20questioned%2