s%20question%2C%20then%3F%20The%20reason%20was%20made%20clear%20by%20Chatterji.%20I%20would%20have%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20IAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20363px)%2085vw%2C%20363px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152159%2FIndias-Experiment-with-Democracy_COVER.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22363%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152159%2FIndias-Experiment-with-Democracy_COVER.jpg%20700w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152159%2FIndias-Experiment-with-Democracy_COVER-194x300.jpg%20194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152159%2FIndias-Experiment-with-Democracy_COVER-662x1024.jpg%20662w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ES.Y.%20Quraishi%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20With%20Democracy%3A%20The%20Life%20of%20a%20Nation%20Through%20Its%20Elections%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%20India%20(October%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20was%20my%20appointment%20as%20an%20election%20commissioner%20conditional%20on%20my%20resignation%20from%20the%20IAS%3F%20Therein%20lies%20the%20important%20constitutional%20principle%20of%20distancing%20the%20EC%20from%20the%20executive%2Fgovernment.%20Importantly%2C%20a%20wall%20was%20built%20between%20me%20and%20the%20PM%20who%20had%20appointed%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20I%20was%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20but%20as%20an%20election%20commissioner%2C%20I%20was%20independent%2C%20neutral%20and%20distant%20from%20him.%20There%20was%20no%20question%20of%20his%20calling%2Fsummoning%20me%20to%20see%20him%20or%20with%20any%20request%2C%20let%20alone%20give%20me%20any%20direction%20or%20instruction.%20He%20could%20appoint%20me%20but%20could%20not%20order%20me%20or%20remove%20me%20because%20of%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20of%20things.%20An%20independent%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20a%20gift%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20the%20nation.%20Free%2C%20fair%20and%20credible%20elections%20are%20sine%20qua%20non%20of%20the%20ECI.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20repeatedly%20stressed%20this%20point%2C%20calling%20the%20Commission%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PMO%E2%80%99s%20summoning%20or%20%E2%80%98inviting%E2%80%99%20of%20not%20just%20the%20CEC%20but%20the%20full%20bench%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20important%20or%20urgent%20the%20issue%20is.%20Let%20alone%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20PM%2C%20even%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20mighty%20PM%20it%20would%20be%20an%20unacceptable%20act.%20Can%20you%20imagine%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20PM%20issuing%20such%20summons%20to%20the%20CJI%2C%20to%20come%20over%20with%20the%20full%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20and%20attend%20a%20meeting%20with%20him%20on%20judicial%20reforms%3F%20The%20secretary%20would%20be%20running%20for%20cover%20with%20a%20contempt%20of%20court%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20the%20neutrality%20and%20independence%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20of%20the%20ECI%20in%20this%20context.%20Both%20are%20independent%20constitutional%20authorities%2C%20deliberately%20separated%20from%20the%20executive.%20Forgetting%20the%20summoning%20of%20the%20CEC%20and%20ECs%2C%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20PM%20cannot%20even%20call%20on%20the%20ECI%20without%20public%20knowledge%20of%20the%20meeting%20and%20what%20transpired%20in%20it.%20Politicians%20of%20all%20hues%20visit%20the%20ECI%20regularly%20with%20petitions%2C%20complaints%20or%20suggestions%2C%20but%20with%20full%20transparency.%20I%20never%20met%20any%20of%20them%20alone%2C%20insisting%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20my%20two%20colleagues.%20Transparency%20is%20the%20key%20word%20here%2C%20and%20perception%20of%20transparency%20is%20equally%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%20us%20talk%20about%20the%20protocol%20in%20this%20matter%2C%20though%20that%20is%20secondary.%20The%20CEC%20is%20very%20high%20in%20the%20warrant%20of%20precedence%E2%80%94%20ninth%E2%80%94while%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20PM%20is%20twenty-third.%20How%20can%20such%20a%20high-ranking%20constitutional%20functionary%20be%20summoned%20to%20attend%20a%20meeting%20with%20an%20officer%2C%20howsoever%20high%20and%20mighty%3F%20The%20law%20ministry%2C%20which%20advises%20the%20government%20on%20all%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20matters%2C%20should%20have%20known%20better%20than%20to%20convey%20that%20it%20was%20okay%20for%20the%20PMO%20to%20%E2%80%98expect%E2%80%99%20the%20CEC%2FECs%20to%20attend%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20recall%20another%20event.%20One%20day%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20Veerappa%20Moily%2C%20the%20then%20law%20minister%3A%20%E2%80%98Mr%20Quraishi%2C%20you%20have%20been%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20electoral%20reforms.%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20come%20for%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20in%20my%20office%20so%20that%20we%20discuss%20them%3F%E2%80%99%20I%20was%20in%20a%20fix%2C%20but%20only%20for%20six%20seconds.%20My%20going%20there%20would%20have%20been%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20declined%20the%20invite.%20Instead%2C%20I%20told%20the%20honourable%20minister%2C%20%E2%80%98Sir%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20your%20kind%20offer%20but%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20come%20over%20instead%3F%20I%20will%20introduce%20you%20to%20my%20brother%20commissioners%20and%20senior%20officers.%E2%80%99%20Gracious%20as%20he%20was%2C%20Moily%20came%20over%20the%20next%20day%20with%20four%20of%20his%20top%20officers.%20What%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20short%20semi-courtesy%20meeting%20went%20on%20for%20over%20three%20hours.%20He%20asked%20whether%20we%20would%20like%20to%20join%20the%20ministry%20in%20hosting%20seven%20regional%20conferences%20to%20build%20a%20national%20consensus%20on%20electoral%20reforms.%20We%20readily%20agreed.%20When%20all%20the%20regional%20meetings%20were%20over%2C%20the%20law%20minister%20came%20over%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20a%20second%20time%20to%20discuss%20the%20arrangements%20for%20the%20final%2C%20national%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20reforms%20were%20materializing%2C%20Moily%20was%20shifted%20to%20another%20ministry%20and%20replaced%20by%20Salman%20Khurshid.%20I%20called%20up%20the%20PM%20to%20protest%E2%80%94just%20when%20Moily%20had%20built%20up%20a%20national%20consensus%2C%20you%20have%20transferred%20him%2C%20undoing%20all%20his%20and%20our%20work%20of%20six%20months%2C%20I%20told%20him.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Salman%20will%20carry%20forward%20this%20work.%20I%20will%20send%20him%20to%20you.%E2%80%99%20Note%20that%20the%20PM%20did%20not%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Go%20and%20meet%20him.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20Khurshid%20came%20over%20to%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20office%20within%20a%20week%20and%20reassured%20us%20about%20taking%20the%20reforms%20forward.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20the%20proposal%20fizzled%20out.%20The%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20Union%20law%20minister%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20ministry%20and%20sanctions%20our%20budget%2C%20visited%20the%20ECI%20thrice%20in%20four%20months%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20reaction%20of%20horror%20and%20disgust%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20at%20being%20called%20over%20to%20the%20PMO%20was%20most%20heartening%2C%20and%20I%20salute%20them.%20But%20why%20they%20got%20persuaded%20to%20attend%20the%20%E2%80%98informal%20interaction%E2%80%99%20subsequently%20puzzles%20me.%20A%20meeting%20with%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20PM%2C%20formal%20or%20informal%2C%20online%20or%20in%20the%20PMO%20or%20at%20the%20ECI%20office%20just%20before%20elections%20raises%20unnecessary%20suspicion.%20Who%20knows%20what%20was%20discussed.%20The%20election%20dates%3F%20Or%20something%20else%3F%20This%20incident%20is%20a%20transgression%20that%20should%20not%20happen%20again.%20The%20arm%E2%80%99s-length%20distance%20envisaged%20in%20the%20Constitution%20for%20interactions%20between%20certain%20institutions%20is%20sacrosanct.%20It%20should%20not%20only%20be%20maintained%20but%20also%20%E2%80%98seen%E2%80%99%20to%20be%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Chr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20S.Y.%20Quraishi%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20With%20Democracy%3A%20The%20Life%20of%20a%20Nation%20Through%20Its%20Elections%3Cem%3E%2C%20published%20with%20permission%20from%20HarperCollins%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696653018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152712%2FElection-Commission-of-India-Photo-PTI1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Felection-commission-neutral-transparent-sy-quraishi-book-excerpt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PMO%E2%80%99s%20summoning%20or%20%E2%80%98inviting%E2%80%99%20of%20election%20commissioners%20in%20December%202021%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20important%20or%20urgent%20the%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Felection-commission-neutral-transparent-sy-quraishi-book-excerpt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20Viral%20pics%20of%20the%20week%22%2C%22c