-demands-an-apology-after-cyprus-arrests-a-russian-journalist-reportedly-for-security-reasons%2Farticleshow%2F104229450.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-demands-an-apology-after-cyprus-arrests-a-russian-journalist-reportedly-for-security-reasons%2Famp_articleshow%2F104229450.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-demands-an-apology-after-cyprus-arrests-a-russian-journalist-reportedly-for-security-reasons%2Famp_articleshow%2F104229450.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Last%20Date%20To%20Exchange%20Rs%202%2C000%20Notes%20At%20Banks%20Today%3A%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20date%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%20at%20the%20bank%20is%20today.%20According%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20after%20October%207%2C%20the%20exchange%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20currency%20notes%20will%20only%20be%20allowed%20at%20the%2019%20RBI%20Issue%20Offices%2C%20with%20a%20cash%20deposit%20limit%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20note%20maximum%20per%20transaction.%20But%20at%20any%20of%20the%2019%20RBI%20Issue%20Offices%2C%20people%20can%20present%20Rs%202%2C000%20banknotes%20for%20credit%20to%20any%20amount%20on%20their%20Indian%20bank%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%20after%20today's%20deadline%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RBI%2C%20the%20Rs%202%2C000%20currency%20note%20will%20remain%20legal%20tender%20even%20after%20the%20October%207%20deadline%2C%20however%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20accepted%20for%20transactions.%20After%20today%2C%20the%20notes%20can%20only%20be%20exchanged%20with%20the%20RBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2FScripts%2FFAQView.aspx%3FId%3D157%5C%22%3ERBI%20FAQs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rs%202000%20banknotes%20can%20continue%20to%20be%20exchanged%20by%20individuals%2Fentities%20at%20the%2019%20RBI%20Issue%20Offices%20up%20to%20a%20limit%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20at%20a%20time.%20Individuals%2FEntities%20can%20also%20tender%20Rs%202000%20banknotes%20at%20the%2019%20RBI%20Issue%20Offices%20for%20credit%20to%20their%20bank%20accounts%20in%20India%20for%20any%20amount%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20exchange%20or%20credit%20shall%20be%20subject%20to%20relevant%20RBI%2C%20Government%20regulations%2C%20submission%20of%20valid%20identity%20documents%20and%20due%20diligence%20as%20deemed%20fit%20by%20RBI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2FScripts%2FBS_PressReleaseDisplay.aspx%3Fprid%3D56475%5C%22%3Epress%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20have%20the%20facility%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202000%20notes%20at%2019%20Regional%20Offices%20(ROs)%20of%20the%20RBI.%20The%2019%20RBI%20issue%20offices%20include%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20Belapur%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Jammu%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Patna%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20one%20can%20also%20exchange%20Rs%202000%20banknotes%20at%20any%20nearby%20bank%20branch.%20Individuals%2FEntities%20from%20within%20the%20country%20can%20also%20send%20Rs%202%2C000%20banknotes%20through%20India%20Post%2C%20addressed%20to%20any%20of%20the%2019%20RBI%20Issue%20Offices%20for%20credit%20to%20their%20bank%20accounts%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RBI's%20guidelines%2C%20as%20these%20notes%20are%20legal%20tender%2C%20the%20exchange%20should%20be%20done%20without%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20request%20slip%20or%20ID%20proof.%20However%2C%20some%20public%20sector%20banks%20have%20implemented%20a%20different%20approach.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20advisable%20to%20have%20an%20ID%20proof%20handy%20when%20exchanging%20this%20currency%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20RBI%20started%20printing%20the%20Rs%202%2C000%20note%20in%20November%202016%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20scrapped%20high-value%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20Rs%20500%20notes%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20RBI%20announced%20that%20about%2096%25%20of%20the%20Rs%202%2C000%20banknotes%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20banking%20system%20since%20the%20central%20bank%20in%20May%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20the%20high-value%20note%20from%20circulation.%20This%20has%20left%20only%20Rs%200.14%20lakh%20crore%20worth%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%20in%20circulation%20till%20September%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696649760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-11%2Frs-2000-notes-afp_650x400_61479281302.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flast-date-to-exchange-rs-2-000-notes-at-banks-today-all-you-need-to-know-4458321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20last%20date%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%20at%20the%20bank%20is%20today.%20According%20to%20RBI%2C%20the%20Rs%202%2C000%20currency%20note%20will%20remain%20legal%20tender%20even%20after%20the%20October%207%20deadline%2C%20however%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20accepted%20for%20transactions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flast-date-to-exchange-rs-2-000-notes-at-banks-today-all-you-need-to-know-4458321%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flast-date-to-exchange-rs-2-000-notes-at-banks-today-all-you-need-to-know-4458321%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-