20few%20more%20medals%20are%20alreadya%20ssured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20outing%20for%20the%20Indian%20women%20as%20Chinese%20Taipei%20pushed%20them%20to%20the%20limit%20in%20the%20final%2C%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20top%20prize%20by%20just%20a%20solitary%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20showed%20nerves%20of%20steel%20in%20the%20last%20two%20raids%20to%20seal%20the%20contest%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20a%20five-point%20lead%20going%20into%20halftime%2C%20courtesy%20of%20a%20super%20raid%20from%20Pooja%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20stars%20of%20the%20intense%20title%20showdown%20that%20also%20saw%20the%20team's%20coach%20being%20cautioned%20with%20a%20green%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAND%20THAT%20IS%20MEDAL%20%23100%20FOR%20!!!%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20HISTORY%20IS%20MADE%20AS%20INDIA%20GETS%20ITS%20100%20MEDAL%20AT%20THE%20ASIAN%20GAMES%202022!%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20This%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20dreams%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20teamwork%20of%20our%20athletes%20involved%20in%20the%20achievement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTEAMINDIA%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TEAMINDIA%3C%2Fa%3E!%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Let%20this%20achievement%20inspire%20generations%20to...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEuBQpvvVQ3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEuBQpvvVQ3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20SAI%20Media%20(%40Media_SAI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMedia_SAI%2Fstatus%2F1710481718476669202%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20won%2070%20medals%20in%20the%20last%20edition%20in%20Indonesia%20where%20the%20country's%20athletes%20won%2016%20gold%2C%2023%20silver%20and%2031%20bronze%20medals%20to%20record%20their%20best-ever%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20back%20of%20a%20splendid%20show%20by%20the%20shooters%20(22)%20and%20track%20and%20field%20athletes%20(29%20medals)%2C%20who%20contributed%2051%20medals%2C%20India%20had%20already%20surpassed%20its%20best-ever%20show%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20won%20many%20surprise%20medals%2C%20the%20biggest%20being%20a%20women's%20table%20tennis%20team%20bronze%20by%20Sutirtha%20Mukherjee%20and%20Ayhika%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20humbled%20the%20mighty%20China%20in%20the%20semifinals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParul%20Chaudhary's%20sensational%20dash%20in%20the%20last%2030%20metres%20of%20the%20women's%205000m%20event%20will%20also%20be%20remembered%20for%20a%20long%20time%20as%20the%20Meerut%20runner%20snatched%20a%20gold%20by%20edging%20Japan's%20Ririka%20Hironaka%20in%20a%20close%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJavelin%20thrower%20Kishore%20Kumar%20Jena's%20astonishing%2086.77m%20throw%20that%20gave%20him%20lead%20over%20superstar%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20in%20the%20men's%20javelin%20event%20was%20another%20unforgettable%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20Chopra%20won%20the%20gold%2C%20while%20Jena%20finished%20behind%20him%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanoers%20Arjun%20Singh%20and%20Sunil%20Singh%20Salam's%20historic%20bronze%20in%20the%20men's%20double%201000m%20along%20with%20Ram%20Baboo%20and%20Manju%20Rani's%20third%20place%20finish%20in%20the%20mixed%2035km%20race%20walk%20were%20perfect%20examples%20that%20if%20athletes%20refuse%20to%20bow%20down%20to%20the%20hardships%20life%20throws%2C%20excelling%20in%20sports%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696648140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fa854efk8_indian-mens-hockey-team-twitter_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fits