2%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Key%20Nuclear%20Secrets%20Trump%20Allegedly%20Leaked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20accused%20of%20leaking%20US%20secrets%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20allegations%20against%20him%20involve%20key%20details%20about%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sensitive%20weapons%20in%20the%20US%20nuclear%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20gave%20key%20details%20on%20the%20US%20Navy's%20elite%20submarine%20fleet%20-%20including%20the%20number%20of%20nuclear%20warheads%20they%20can%20carry%20and%20how%20close%20they%20can%20get%20to%20Russian%20vessels%20without%20being%20detected%20-%20to%20Australian%20billionaire%20Anthony%20Pratt%2C%20who%20passed%20the%20information%20on%20to%20dozens%20of%20friends%20and%20contacts%2C%20according%20to%20ABC%20News%20and%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20disclosure%20is%20only%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20cases%20that%20raise%20grave%20questions%20about%20Trump's%20willingness%20to%20keep%20the%20nation's%20secrets%20-%20an%20issue%20that's%20only%20going%20to%20remain%20front%20and%20center%20given%20his%20commanding%20lead%20in%20the%20polls%20to%20secure%20the%20Republican%20nomination%20to%20challenge%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20again%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20few%20people%20in%20the%20US%20government%20know%20the%20exact%20configuration%20of%20the%20nuclear%20subs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joe%20Cirincione%2C%20a%20security%20analyst%20who%20held%20the%20highest%20clearance%20level%20when%20he%20worked%20in%20Congress%20on%20nuclear%20weapons%20issues.%20If%20true%2C%20Trump's%20disclosure%20gets%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20US%20capabilities%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20knew%20the%20exact%20payload%20of%20our%20nuclear%20subs%20nor%20the%20details%20of%20our%20anti-submarine%20warfare%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Cirincione%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20need%20to%20know.%20The%20Australian%20billionaire%20didn't%20have%20a%20need%20to%20know%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20already%20battling%20a%20federal%20indictment%20on%2040%20counts%20of%20allegedly%20holding%20on%20to%20classified%20documents%20at%20his%20Florida%20mansion%20after%20he%20left%20office%2C%20disclosing%20details%20of%20war%20plans%20to%20civilians%2C%20and%20obstructing%20government%20efforts%20to%20get%20the%20documents%20back.%20Those%20documents%20-%20which%20included%20assessments%20from%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency%20-%20were%20purportedly%20left%20unattended%20in%20a%20bathroom%20and%20on%20a%20ballroom%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20early%20in%20his%20presidency%20in%202017%2C%20reports%20said%20Trump%20revealed%20sensitive%20intelligence%20information%20from%20Israel%20to%20Russia's%20foreign%20minister%20and%20ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20Trump%20called%20the%20submarine%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20that%20he%20was%20only%20telling%20Pratt%20that%20the%20US%20makes%20the%20best%20military%20equipment%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20called%20the%20claim%20a%20bid%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20will%20also%20only%20further%20underscore%20the%20deep%20and%20growing%20unease%20among%20allies%20about%20the%20US's%20ability%20to%20keep%20intelligence%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20especially%20if%20Trump%20wins%20re-election.%20Allied%20doubts%20have%20only%20been%20confirmed%20after%20a%20series%20of%20hacks%20allegedly%20committed%20by%20US%20adversaries%20such%20as%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20and%20leaks%20from%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20an%20information%20sharing%20arrangement%20in%20effect%20and%20then%20information%20is%20disclosed%20in%20an%20inappropriate%20way%2C%20there's%20every%20reason%20to%20think%20that%20people%20are%20going%20to%20be%20reluctant%20to%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bradley%20Martin%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20the%20Navy%20after%2030%20years%20and%20is%20now%20a%20senior%20policy%20researcher%20at%20RAND%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPratt%20is%20one%20of%20more%20than%2080%20people%20that%20Special%20Counsel%20Jack%20Smith's%20office%20identified%20as%20potential%20trial%20witnesses%20in%20the%20classified%20documents%20case%20in%20Florida%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20who%20wasn't%20authorized%20to%20discuss%20it%20publicly.%20He%20was%20interviewed%20at%20least%20twice%20this%20year%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20according%20to%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSharing%20top%20secret%20details%20not%20only%20threatens%20that%20stealth%20advantage%20but%20puts%20the%20lives%20of%20Sailors%20at%20risk%20and%20undermines%20our%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Representative%20Joe%20Courtney%2C%20a%20Connecticut%20Democrat%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExperts%20on%20US%20submarine%20technology%20said%20Trump's%20disclosures%2C%20if%20true%2C%20could%20expose%20key%20details%20about%20its%20submarines'%20tactical%20abilities.%20The%20US%20Navy%20refuses%20to%20confirm%20or%20deny%20the%20presence%20or%20number%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20on%20certain%20vessels.%20And%20telling%20others%20how%20close%20subs%20can%20get%20to%20adversaries%20could%20erode%20US%20attack%20submarines'%20tactical%20advantage%20as%20they%20evade%20and%20stalk%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sub%20silencing%20data%20is%20very%20hush%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hans%20Kristensen%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Federation%20of%20American%20Scientists%20Nuclear%20Information%20Project.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20gone%20to%20jail%20for%20revealing%20that%20kind%20of%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERand's%20Martin%20said%20he%20doubts%20whether%20the%20secrets%20will%20disadvantage%20the%20Navy.%20The%20number%20of%20warheads%20on%20a%20US%20submarine%20likely%20wouldn't%20surprise%20rivals%20such%20as%20Russia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20always%20working%20to%20make%20submarines%20quieter%20in%20ways%20that%20might%20render%20Trump's%20information%20out%20of%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20military%20will%20take%20actions%20to%20mitigate%20the%20damage%2C%20Martin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20be%20doing%20that%20every%2010%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E--With%20assistance%20from%20Tony%20Capaccio%20and%20Zoe%20Tillman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696646700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fgv9q64r8_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-leaked-key-details-about-us-nuclear-weapons-report-4458268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20accused%20of%20leaking%20US%20secrets%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20allegations%20against%20him%20involve%20key%20details%20about%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sensitive%20weapons%20in%20the%20US%20nuclear%20arsenal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-leaked-key-details-about-us-nuclear-weapons-report-4458268%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-leaked-key-details-about-us-nuclear-weapons-report-4458268%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-le