%20According%20to%20the%20official%20site%2C%20Arnav%20Daga%20spent%2041%20days%20using%20playing%20cards%20to%20create%20four%20iconic%20buildings%20from%20his%20home%20city%20-%20the%20Writers'%20Building%2C%20the%20Shaheed%20Minar%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20Stadium%2C%20and%20St.%20Paul's%20Cathedral.%20He%20used%20around%20143%2C000%20playing%20cards%20and%20zero%20tape%20and%20glue.%20His%20finished%20project%20measured%2040%20feet%20in%20length%2C%2011%20feet%204%20inches%20in%20height%20and%2016%20feet%208%20inches%20in%20width.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20blog%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fteen-stacks-143-000-playing-cards-to-create-worlds-largest-card-structure-759373%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUsing%2520around%2520143%252C000%2520playing%2520cards%2Ctook%252041%2520days%2520to%2520complete.%5C%22%3EGWR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Arnav%20broke%20the%20previous%20world%20record%20held%20by%20Bryan%20Berg%2C%20whose%20playing%20card%20structure%20of%20three%20Macao%20hotels%20measured%2034%20feet%20and%201%20inch%20long%2C%209%20feet%20and%205%20inches%20tall%20and%2011%20feet%20and%207%20inches%20wide.%20Talking%20about%20his%20project%2C%20the%2015-year-old%20said%20that%20before%20commencing%20the%20card%20construction%2C%20he%20visited%20all%20four%20sites%20to%20study%20their%20architecture%20and%20work%20out%20their%20dimensions%20closely.%20He%20then%20viewed%20around%2030%20places%20to%20find%20a%20suitable%20site%20for%20his%20own%20%26quot%3Bcard-chitecture%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fzg4OkrefKDs%3Fsi%3DRKesLaKIPMSuUelH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArnav's%20%26quot%3Btechnique%20involves%20using%20%26quot%3Bgrids%26quot%3B%20(four%20horizontal%20cards%20stood%20at%20right%20angles)%20and%20%26quot%3Bvertical%20cells%26quot%3B%20(four%20vertical%20cards%20inclined%20towards%20each%20other%20at%20right%20angles)%2C%26quot%3B%20GWR%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20said%20his%2041-day%20process%20was%20slowed%20when%20the%20Shaheed%20Minar%20kept%20falling%20down.%20He%20%26quot%3Bimprovised%26quot%3B%20a%20lot.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20frustrating%20that%20so%20many%20hours%20and%20days%20of%20work%20got%20wiped%20out%20and%20I%20had%20to%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%20but%20for%20me%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnav%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2015-year-old%20struggled%20to%20balance%20his%20schoolwork%20and%20record%20attempts%20throughout%20the%2041%20days.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20tough%20to%20do%20both%2C%20but%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20overcome%20all%20difficulties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fed-sheeran-explains-his-decision-to-dig-his-own-grave-4457037%5C%22%3EEd%20Sheeran%20Explains%20His%20Decision%20To%20Dig%20His%20Own%20Grave%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20GWR%2C%20Arnav%20has%20been%20card%20stacking%20since%20he%20was%20eight%20years%20old.%20He%20began%20to%20take%20it%20more%20seriously%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%202020%2C%20as%20he%20found%20himself%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20time%20to%20practise%20his%20passion.%20Due%20to%20having%20limited%20space%20in%20his%20room%2C%20he%20began%20by%20creating%20smaller%20structures%2C%20some%20of%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20arnavinnovates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20practise%20in%20making%20smaller%20structures%20improved%20my%20skill%20and%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20for%20attempting%20a%20world%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnav%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20definitely%20overwhelming%20and%20feels%20like%20I%20am%20living%20my%20dream%20which%20I%20saw%20back%20in%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20GWR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696646160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd5v6hrcg_arnav-daga_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fkolkata-boy-15-sets-guinness-world-record-by-creating-largest-playing-card-structure-4458261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2015-year-old%20boy%20from%20Kolkata%20has%20set%20a%20new%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20(GWR)%20for%20creating%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20largest%20playing%20card%20structure%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A106%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fkolkata-boy-15-sets-guinness-world-record-by-creating-largest-playing-card-structure-4458261%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fkolkata-boy-15-sets-guinness-world-record-by-creating-largest-playing-card-structure-4458261%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fkolkata-boy-15-sets-guinness-world-record-by-creating-largest-playing-card-structure-4458261%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20tribute%20to%20M%20S%20Swaminathan%3A%20A%20true%20'farmers'%20scientist'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696646152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F28%2Ffull%2F1695885132-4221.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-tribute-to-m-s-swaminathan-a-true-farmers-scientist-123100601492_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Swaminathan%20has%20nurtured%20countless%20minds%2C%20instilling%20in%20them%20a%20passion%20for%20learning%20and%20innovation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-tribute-to-m-s-swami