hoto%2F104227371.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20granted%20a%20temporary%20delay%20in%20canceling%20his%20business%20licenses%20in%20New%20York%2C%20after%20an%20appeal%20was%20filed%20to%20halt%20the%20trial.%20The%20trial%2C%20which%20began%20on%20Monday%2C%20follows%20a%20ruling%20last%20month%20that%20there%20had%20been%20repeated%20fraud%20by%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%20While%20the%20trial%20will%20not%20be%20suspended%2C%20a%20stay%20has%20been%20granted%20on%20the%20order%20to%20cancel%20the%20business%20certificates.%20The%20trial%20is%20set%20to%20resume%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20New%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20seeking%20a%20%24250%20million%20judgment%20against%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnew-york-judge-orders-hold-on-canceling-trumps-business-licenses%2Farticleshow%2F104227371.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnew-york-judge-orders-hold-on-canceling-trumps-business-licenses%2Famp_articleshow%2F104227371.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnew-york-judge-orders-hold-on-canceling-trumps-business-licenses%2Famp_articleshow%2F104227371.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2253%20Killed%20In%20Sikkim%20Floods%2C%2027%20Bodies%20Found%20In%20Teesta%20River%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EOver%20140%20people%20are%20still%20missing%2C%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced.%20The%20Sikkim%20government%20has%20reported%20that%201%2C173%20houses%20have%20been%20severely%20damaged%20and%202%2C413%20people%20have%20been%20rescued.%20All%20bridges%20downstream%20to%20the%20Teesta-V%20hydropower%20station%20have%20been%20submerged%20or%20washed%20out%2C%20disrupting%20communication%20to%20North%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESikkim%20Chief%20Minister%20Prem%20Singh%20Tamang%20chaired%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20yesterday%20to%20chalk%20out%20rescue%2C%20relief%2C%20and%20restoration%20strategies.%20Priority%20has%20been%20given%20to%20opening%20the%20road%20connectivity%20up%20to%20Chungthang%2C%20while%20the%20road%20from%20Naga%20to%20Toong%20will%20be%20constructed%20subject%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20land%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Compensation%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20has%20been%20announced%20for%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESikkim%20authorities%20are%20prioritising%20reopening%20road%20connectivity%20to%20Chungthang%20and%20building%20the%20road%20from%20Naga%20to%20Toong%20subject%20to%20land%20availability.%20Throughout%20the%20day%2C%20officers%20from%20different%20departments%20met%20with%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20to%20update%20him%20on%20the%20status%20of%20road%20connectivity%2C%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%2C%20and%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20predicted%20light%20to%20moderate%20rainfall%20in%20most%20places%20in%20Mangan%20district%20over%20the%20next%20five%20days%2C%20with%20generally%20cloudy%20to%20overcast%20skies%20in%20Lachen%20and%20Lachung.%20This%20makes%20airlifting%20over%203%2C000%20stranded%20tourists%20challenging.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%20reported%20that%20multiple%20attempts%20to%20carry%20out%20rescue%20and%20relief%20operations%20with%20Mi-17%20helicopters%20have%20been%20unsuccessful%20for%20the%20past%20two%20days%20due%20to%20bad%20weather%2C%20low%20cloud%20cover%2C%20and%20low%20visibility%20in%20the%20Lachen%20and%20Lachung%20valleys.%20The%20aerial%20rescue%20operations%20are%20expected%20to%20resume%20early%20morning%20today%20if%20the%20weather%20permits.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EFlash%20floods%20cloudburst%20have%20ravaged%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20affecting%20over%2025%2C000%20people%2C%20damaging%20nearly%201%2C200%20homes%2C%20and%20destroying%2013%20bridges.%20Rescue%20workers%20have%20saved%202%2C413%20people%20so%20far%2C%20but%206%2C875%20people%20remain%20displaced%20and%20are%20sheltering%20in%2022%20relief%20camps%20across%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20glacial%20lake%20burst%20triggered%20flash%20floods%20and%20released%20water%20from%20Chungthang%20Dam%2C%20drastically%20increasing%20the%20water%20level%20of%20the%20Teesta%20River%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20causing%20widespread%20devastation%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Himalayan%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BRoad%20connectivity%20between%20the%20districts%20has%20been%20cut%20off%20and%20bridges%20have%20been%20washed%20away.%20Communication%20in%20North%20Sikkim%20has%20been%20severely%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Tamang%20said%2C%20blaming%20%26quot%3Binferior%20construction%26quot%3B%20by%20previous%20state%20governments%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Chungthang%20Dam.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20NDTV%20learnt%20that%20a%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20had%20flagged%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20meteorological%20and%20monitoring%20stations%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20regions.%20On%20March%2029%2C%20Sikkim%20was%20told%20in%20Parliament%20that%20it%20has%20694%20glacial%20lakes%20and%20eight%20flood%20forecasting%20stations%2C%20three%20for%20water%20levels%20and%20five%20for%20inflows.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20approved%20the%20release%20of%20Rs%2044.8%20crore%20in%20advance%20from%20the%20central%20share%20of%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Fund%20(SDRF)%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20floods.%20The%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20also%20formed%20an%20Inter-Ministerial%20Central%20Team%20(IMCT)%20to%20visit%20the%20affected%20areas%20and%20assess%20the%20damage.%3C%