0for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20that%20Texans%20are%20used%20to%20that%20though.%20When%20the%20ice%20storm%20hit%20and%20we%20had%20no%20electricity%20and%20our%20water%20was%20contaminated%20everyone%20said%2C%20no%20problem%2C%20come%20to%20my%20house%2C%20I%20have%20water.%20We%20worked%20together.%20But%20nobody%20had%20any%20concept%20of%20wondering%20why%20the%20state%20wasn't%20helping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20have%20had%20to%20accept%20that%20things%20are%20wilder%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20regards%20to%20crime%2C%20it's%20night%20and%20day.%20Crime%20is%20not%20dealt%20with%20in%20California.%20They%20just%20kind%20of%20look%20the%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20absolutely%20not%20true%20in%20Texas.%20And%20that's%20a%20big%20deal%20to%20me.%20I'm%20by%20myself%20with%20my%20son%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20place%20where%20I%20don't%20feel%20safe.%20I%20never%20felt%20safe%20in%20southern%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20photos%20of%20janelle%20crossan%20holding%20keys%20to%20her%20new%20house%20and%20her%20son%20playing%20in%20the%20snow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652098806561dd877e73e5bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJanelle%20Crossan%20said%20she%20feels%20like%20she%20can%20be%20her%20authentic%20self%20in%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Janelle%20Crossan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20miss%20the%20weather%20in%20California.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20absolutely%20gorgeous%20there.%20I%20lived%20right%20by%20the%20beach.%20Here%20we%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20crazy%20storms.%20You%20never%20know%20what%20the%20weather%20is%20going%20to%20do.%20It's%20something%20you%20have%20to%20battle%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20miss%20the%20food%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20It's%20like%20no%20other.%20You%20just%20can't%20