0be%20charged'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gary%20wang%20sam%20bankman%20fried%20trial%20court%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65206ba09f7ca8b2bbdc823f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGary%20Wang%20testifies%20during%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20fraud%20trial%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20FTX%2C%20the%20bankrupt%20cryptocurrency%20exchange.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FJane%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EGary%20Wang%20agreed%20to%20cooperate%20with%20prosecutors%20in%20his%20first%20meeting%20with%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20jurors%20at%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20trial%20that%20he%20knew%20what%20they%20did%20at%20FTX%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20charged%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20shorter%20prison%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20testified%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Wang%20and%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years.%20The%20two%20met%20at%20a%20math%20camp%20in%20their%20high%20school%20years%20and%20later%20lived%20together%20while%20attending%20MIT%20before%20co-founding%20FTX%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20only%20six%20days%20after%20FTX's%20bankruptcy%20for%20Wang%20to%20tell%20federal%20prosecutors%20he%20wanted%20to%20cooperate%20with%20their%20criminal%20investigation%20into%20his%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20charged%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20shorter%20prison%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%2C%20FTX's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20implosion%2C%20testified%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20on%20Friday%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20the%2030-year-old%20Wang%20detailed%20his%20experience%20working%20with%20Bankman-Fried%20at%20FTX%20and%20explained%20how%20deeply%20its%20funds%20were%20commingled%20with%20Alameda%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFTX%20collapsed%20after%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Alameda%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20also%20controlled%20%E2%80%94%20had%20taken%20enormous%20losses%20on%20risky%20bets%20with%20funds%20from%20ordinary%20FTX%20customers.%20Prosecutors%20accused%20Bankman-Fried%20of%20fraud%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20declared%C2%A0bankruptcy%20on%20November%2010%2C%202022%2C%20and%20its%20servers%20were%20shut%20down%20the%20next%20morning.%20Wang%20testified%20that%20he%20spent%20November%2011%20and%2012%20dealing%20with%20regulators%20in%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20where%20FTX%20was%20based%2C%20and%20working%20with%20US-based%20lawyers%20to%20identify%20assets%20in%20different%20accounts%20that%20could%20be%20restored%20to%20customers%20and%20any%20other%20creditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gary%20Wang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651733bc846a2f0019a11b7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGary%20Wang.%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20from%20the%20Bahamas%20on%20November%2013%2C%20meeting%20with%20the%20FBI%20and%20prosecutors%20on%20November%2017.%20At%20the%20very%20first%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20cooperate%20with%20the%20prosecutors'%20criminal%20investigation%2C%20he%20testified.%20He%20met%20with%20investigators%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20times%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Funited-states-attorney-announces-extradition-ftx-founder-samuel-bankma