0marketing.%20It's%20become%20about%20driving%20purpose%20and%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMichael%20Park%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20ServiceNow%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Michael%20Park%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20ServiceNow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65173e305640b20019d784fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Park%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20ServiceNow%3Cp%3EServiceNow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPark%20joined%20ServiceNow%20in%202020%20and%20was%20promoted%20to%20CMO%20in%20January%2C%202022.%20Previously%20he%20held%20executive%20positions%20at%20such%20companies%20as%20Eagle%20View%2C%20HP%2C%20and%20Microsoft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPark%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20on%20video%20about%20how%20he%20came%20to%20marketing%20via%20a%20non-traditional%20path%2C%20having%20run%20sales%20and%20product%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20marketing%20profession%20is%20by%20far%20and%20away%20the%20most%20complex%20function%20I've%20ever%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20diversity%20of%20the%20skillsets%2C%20ranging%20from%20the%20highest%20order%20of%20creative%20to%20the%20highest%20order%20of%20data%20science%20and%20every%20flavor%20in%20between.%20You've%20got%20a%20number%20of%20functions%20that%20you've%20got%20to%20align%20with%20seamless%20precision.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20marketing%20leaders%20have%20to%20embrace%20rapid%20change%2C%20citing%20how%20quickly%20businesses%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20ricochet%20between%20geopolitical%20issues%2C%20inflation%20worries%2C%20and%20the%20frontier%20of%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20that%20is%20a%20certainty%20right%20now%20is%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20the%20world.%20Understand%20the%20situation%20you%20are%20in%20and%20lean%20into%20the%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERaja%20Rajamannar%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20and%20president%2C%20healthcare%2C%20Mastercard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222070%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raja%20Rajamannar%2C%20cheif%20marketing%20officer%2C%20Mastercard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6517203d846a2f0019a11505%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaja%20Rajamannar%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20Mastercard%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERajamannar%20was%20named%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%20at%20Mastercard%20ten%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20September%2C%202023.%20He%20is%20also%20president%20of%20the%20company's%20healthcare%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BQuantum%20Marketing%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20bestseller%2C%20and%20Rajamannar%20will%20be%20writing%20a%20regular%20column%20for%20CMO%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Insider%20during%20Cannes%20Lions%2C%20Rajamannar%20said%20that%20digital%20innovation%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20change%20has%20made%20sourcing%20and%20retaining%20talent%20more%20difficult..%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20easy%20to%20attract%20the%20best%20of%20the%20talent%20who%20are%20very%20competent%20and%20capable%20of%20both%20right-brain%20thinking%20and%20left-brain%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERajamannar%20said%20that%20more%20of%20Mastercard's%20marketing%20dollars%20have%20been%20directed%20increasingly%20to%20experiential%20channels%20and%20esports%2C%20the%20kinds%20of%20activations%20that%20demand%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20c-suite%20presence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20be%20at%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20CEO%2C%20you%20don't%20behave%20as%20the%20head%20of%20marketing%2C%2