20it%20clear%20that%20Singham%20acted%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20China%2C%20since%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20active%20member%20of%20the%20propaganda%20wing%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20two%20Chinese%20telecom%20companies%2C%20Xiaomi%20and%20Vivo%2C%20helped%20execute%20this%20conspiracy%20by%20setting%20up%20%E2%80%9Cthousands%20of%20shell%20companies%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinfusing%20foreign%20funds%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20police%20have%20arrested%20Purkayastha%20and%20another%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20employee%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law.%20Phones%20and%20computers%20have%20been%20seized%20from%20over%2050%20other%20individuals%2C%20most%20of%20them%20journalists.%20Without%20going%20into%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20police%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20charges%20themselves%20allows%20us%20to%20raise%20several%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20seriousness%20in%20unearthing%20and%20prosecuting%20all%20the%20conspirators%20allegedly%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20Has%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20requested%20the%20United%20States%20government%20to%20take%20action%20against%20and%2For%20extradite%20its%20citizen%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20whose%20financing%20of%20NewsClick%20is%20being%20called%20a%20terrorist%20crime%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20August%2017%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%20authorities%20say%20they%20had%20analysed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20emails%20from%20Purkayastha%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20which%20were%20seized%20two%20years%20earlier%20when%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20first%20raided%20the%20news%20portal%E2%80%99s%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20neither%20before%20or%20after%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%20does%20the%20government%20appear%20to%20have%20made%20any%20efforts%20to%20even%20interrogate%20Singham%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20accused%20number%203%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20is%20supposedly%20the%20financial%20lynchpin%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20be%20because%20the%20government%20knows%20that%20the%20fund%20transfers%20from%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20entities%20are%20exactly%20what%20both%20the%20remitter%20and%20recipient%20have%20said%20they%20are%3A%20a%20bona%20fide%20investment%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fstatement-on-worldwide-media-holdings-investment-in-newsclick%2Farticle67390484.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20using%20money%20generated%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20that%20if%20India%20were%20to%20request%20the%20US%20authorities%20to%20take%20action%20they%20would%20be%20rebuffed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20Has%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20notified%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F1fb7278b-2c6e-4e42-9b45-801bd6b8c21a%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F1fb7278b-2c6e-4e42-9b45-801bd6b8c21a%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696691403262000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0kiTczY9jWX_UP8BxghogA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%3C%2Fa%3E%20secretariat%20in%20Paris%20that%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20and%20his%20companies%20are%20involved%20in%20terror%20financing%20so%20that%20all%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20can%20take%20action%20against%20him%3F%20Does%20it%20intend%20to%20request%20Interpol%20to%20issue%20a%20red-corner%20notice%20against%20the%20businessman%3F%3C%2Fem%