%3Eby%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20other%20foreign%20actors%3C%2Fa%3E%20driven%20by%20disinformation%20and%20other%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20one%20major%20disinformation%20campaign%20around%20the%20Canada-India%20spat%20is%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20found%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20amounts%20of%20cocaine%E2%80%9D%20on%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20aircraft%20in%20Delhi%20and%20that%20this%20was%20the%20reason%20his%20departure%20from%20India%20was%20delayed%20by%20two%20days.%20The%20cocaine%20disinformation%20first%20emerged%20on%20Indian%20right%20wing%20social%20media%20handles%20and%20was%20then%20picked%20up%20by%20a%20retired%20Indian%20diplomat%20on%20live%20news%20television%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexdiplomat-claimed-trudeaus-plane-was-full-of-cocaine-during-india-visit-canada-pm-responds-101695991471048.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprompting%20an%20angry%20denial%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribed%20by%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpro-Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%20outside%20a%20gurudwara%20in%20Canada%20this%20June%20by%20masked%20gunmen%20and%20New%20Delhi%20has%20dismissed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20accusation%20of%20involvement%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%2C%20David%20Cohen%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3Ehad%20later%20said%20that%20inputs%20from%20%E2%80%98five%20eyes%E2%80%99%20intelligence%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20led%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20go%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20v