0independent%20investigating%20agencies%20for%20political%20ends%20against%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20deliberate%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxZYkWDA7CI%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxZYkWDA7CI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20M.K.Stalin%20(%40mkstalin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkstalin%2Fstatus%2F1709820887061639295%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reaction%20from%20Stalin%20came%20even%20as%20the%20tax%20men%20raided%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Adyar%20in%20Chennai%20and%20other%20premises%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20educational%20institutions%20run%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20officials%20also%20raided%20Sri%20Lakshamana%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20in%20Agaram%20in%20neighbouring%20Union%20territory%20of%20Puducherry.%20Jagathrakshakan%20represents%20the%20Arakkonam%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncome%20tax%20officials%20continued%20searches%20in%20the%20house%20and%20business%20premises%20of%20DMK%20MP%20Jagathrakshakan%20for%20the%20second%20day%20today%2C%20Friday%2C%20October%206.%20The%20raid%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20second%20team%20of%20officials%2C%20which%20searched%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Adyar%20in%20Chennai.%20Television%20channels%20showed%20an%20unruffled%20MP%20welcoming%20the%20raiding%20party.%20They%20also%20searched%20a%20brewery%20and%20hotels%20owned%20by%20Jagathrakshakan%20in%20Kancheepuram%2C%2070%20kilometres%20from%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raid%20also%20covered%20relatives%20of%20the%20MP.%20Taxmen%20said%20they%20had%20seized%20cash%20and%20documents%20during%20the%20raids%20in%20over%2040%20locations%20and%20details%20of%20seizures%20would%20be%20disclosed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%20charges%20against%20other%20DMK%20leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJagathrakshakan%20is%20the%20second%20top%20DMK%20leader%20to%20face%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20central%20probe%20agencies.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20arrested%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20and%20DMK%20leader%20Senthil%20Balaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20act%20of%20defiance%2C%20Stalin%20refused%20to%20drop%20Balaji%20from%20the%20Cabinet%2C%20despite%20a%20hastily%20issued%20dismissal%20order%20by%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%2C%20which%20he%20withdrew%20later.%20Ravi%20had%20said%20he%20had%20been%20advised%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fsenthil-balaji-dismissal-what-did-amit-shah-tell-tamil-nadu-governor-rn-ravi-11688117704673.html%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20withdraw%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14085918%2Fdownload-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14085918%2Fdownload-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14085918%2Fdownload-1-300x137.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14085918%2Fdownload-1-1024x468.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657982%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22548%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EV.%20Senthil%20Balaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Stalin%20himself%20had%20levelled%20corruption%20charges%20against%20Senthil%20Balaji%20when%20he%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20government.%20However%2C%20not%20only%20had%20Stalin%20inducted%20him%20into%20his%20party%20but%20also%20made%20him%20a%20minister%2C%20for%20he%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20close%20aide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jagatrathrakshakan%20and%20Senthil%20Balaji%20walked%20over%20to%20DMK%20from%20AIADMK%20following%20the%20demise%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20AIADMK%20chief%20J.%20Jayalalithaa%20in%20December%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVigilance%20cases%20against%20long-time%20DMK%20ministers%20like%20K.%20Ponmudi%2C%20K.K.S.S.R.%20Ramachandran%20and%20Thangam%20Thennarasu%2C%20registered%20during%20the%20previous%20AIADMK%20regime%20between%202016-21%2C%20were%20withdrawn%20by%20Stalin%20after%20he%20came%20to%20power.%20The%20cases%20were%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20corruption%20during%20their%20tenure%20as%20ministers%20in%20the%20AIADMK%20between%202006-11.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20this%20has%20been%20the%20pattern%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20political%20leaders%20alternating%20between%20the%20DMK%20and%20AIADMK.%C2%A0The%20only%20top%20leader%20to%20have%20ever%20been%20convicted%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20is%20AIADMK%20supremo%20Jayalalithaa.%20The%20case%20against%20her%20was%20initiated%20by%20M.%20Karunanidhi%20in%201996%20during%20his%20chief%20ministership.%20After%2018%20years%2C%20it%20ended%20in%20her%20conviction%20by%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20trial%20court%20order%20against%20Jayalalithaa.%20She%20passed%20away%20in%20December%202016.%20The%20apex%20court%20passed%20its%20judgment%20in%20March%202017%2C%20which%20held%20her%20guilty%20of%20amassing%20wealth%20by%20illegal%20means%2C%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2056%20crore.%20Jayalalithaa%E2%80%99s%20aides%2C%20Sasikala%20and%20three%20others%2C%20served%20a%20sentence%20and%20walked%20out%20of%20jail.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20barred%20from%20running%20for%20public%20office%20for%20a%20period%20of%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20introduced%20a%20new%20dimension%20in%20Dravidian%20politics%20by%20using%20Central%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20and%20IT%20against%20state%20ministers.%20Many%20believe%20he%20is%20following%20the%20path%20trodden%20by%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20had%20also%20slapped%20corruption%20cases%20against%20DMK%20patriarch%20M.%20Karunanidhi%20only%20to%20withdraw%20them%20in%20return%20for%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20perception%20that%20Modi%20is%20also%20using%20the%20Central%20agencies%20to%20pressure%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20those%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20into%20submission.%20Corruption%20is%20the%20main%20plank%20he%20is%20using%20in%20every%20state%20in%20his%20battle%20of%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20investigations%20launched%20by%20Central%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20IT%20against%20the%20DMK%20Ministers%20are%20yet%20to%20reach%20trial%20stage%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStalin%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20that%20the%20raids%20against%20DMK%20leaders%20are%20vindictive%2C%20however%2C%20lacks%20moral%20appeal%20as%20he%20himself%20has%20withdrawn%20cases%20registered%20by%20the%20previous%20AIADMK%20regime%20against%20three%20DMK%20ministers%2C%20M.%20Ponmudi%2C%20K.K.S.S.R.%20Ramachandran%2C%20and%20Thangam%20Thennarasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20Madras%20high%20court%20judge%20M.%20Anand%20Venkatesh%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20discharge%20of%20these%20ministers%20from%20corruption%20cases%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiscarriage%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CSomething%20is%20rotten..%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Justice%20Venkatesh%20who%20is%20the%20portfolio%20judge%20for%20special%20courts%20dealing%20with%20corruption%20and%20other%20cases%20against%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDMK%E2%80%99s%20organising%20secretary%20and%20legal%20wing%20in-charge%20R.S.%20Bharathi%20has%20said%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20selective%20approach%20smacks%20of%20discrimination.%20The%20judge%20has%20used%20his%20discretionary%20power%20in%20a%20malafide%20manner%2C%20Bharathi%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20has%20however%20refused%20to%20take%20contempt%20action%20but%20said%20those%20who%20are%20not%20able%20to%20tolerate%20criticism%20are%20unfit%20to%20hold%20public%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20same%20charge%20Stalin%20and%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20now%20leveling%20against%20Modi%20as%20such%20political%20optics%20come%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20that%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20is%20all%20about%20dynasty%20and%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20says%20this%20has%20been%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20against%20the%20opposition%2C%20be%20it%20Kashmir%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20or%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20opposition%20has%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20massive%20%E2%80%9Cwashing%20machine%E2%80%9D.%20Once%20the%20tainted%20politician%20goes%20through%20the%20wringer%2C%20he%20will%20come%20out%20sparkling%20white.%20For%20instance%2C%20Ajay%20Pawar%20was%20accused%20of%20serious%20corruption%20before%20joining%20the%20BJP-alliance%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20However%2C%20Ajay%20Pawar%20is%20now%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Ekanth%20Shinde%2C%20of%20which%20BJP%20is%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20being%20the%20case%2C%20raids%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20means%20to%20poach%20tainted%20DMK%20ministers%20by%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696596258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06180635%2FThe-Wire-30.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-authorities-raid-dmk-mp-jagathrakshakan-vendetta-politics-says-cm-stalin%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jagathrakshakan%20is%20the%2