ry%20killings%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20%3Cem%3ESati%3C%2Fem%3E%20(where%20a%20widow%20would%20end%20her%20life%20by%20jumping%20into%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20pyre)%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20about%20the%20Amendment%20to%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%20and%20the%20Sati%20Prohibition%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20political%20activism%20led%20to%20her%2018-month%20imprisonment%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20She%20established%20the%20Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samiti%20and%20co-authored%20%E2%80%9CWidows%2C%20Abandoned%20and%20Destitute%20Women%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20with%20Jamila%20Verghese%20and%20Dr%20Kumari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20died%20on%2031%20December%202001%2C%20much%20before%20she%20could%20realise%20the%20fruits%20of%20her%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20legislation%20will%20bear%20fruit%20only%20in%202029%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20delimitation%20clause%20in%20the%20bill.%20The%20reservation%20is%20proposed%20to%20be%20implemented%20after%20a%20new%20census%20is%20published%20and%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20is%20completed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20Pramila%E2%80%99s%20dream%20of%20seeing%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20filled%20with%20women%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20six%20more%20years.%20But%2C%20the%2046.1%20crore%20female%20voters%20will%20have%20something%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20the%202029%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnnecessary%20conflicts%20that%20are%20a%20drain%20on%20our%20resources%20will%20stop.%20We%20are%20creators%2C%20not%20destroyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pramila.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpramila-dandavate-first-wom